"<i>In honor of master Heryera, who gave her life in defense of Elensefar "
"against the lich Ras-Tabahn.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>谨以此纪念赫耶拉大师，她为保卫埃仁撒伐，对抗巫妖拉斯-塔班，献出了自己的生"
"命。</i>"

#. [unit]: id=Leollyn
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:182
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:249
