#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. the player has completed their puzzle, and filled the central "mirror pool" with water
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1079
msgid "There! The pool is full!"
msgstr "成了！水池满了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [time]: id=void
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1106
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:926
#, fuzzy
msgid "Void"
msgstr "虚空"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1145
msgid "What was that?!"
msgstr "那是什么？！"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1156
msgid ""
"I think this whole mirror world is starting to fall apart! I have to hurry!"
msgstr "看来这整片镜中世界正开始分崩离析！我必须争分夺秒了！"

#. [message]
#. the player's units have just been transported into a strange realm, and aren't sure what's going on. Kalenz probably knows more than anybody else, and is calling out to see where Elende is (and what exactly she's doing)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1299
msgid "Elende!"
msgstr "艾莲德！"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1304
msgid "Elende, I come with friends, seeking foresight! Deoran and Del—"
msgstr "艾莲德，我携挚友而来，只为求得预知之明！德欧兰与德——"

#. [message]
#. immediately after this, magically created "mirror image" units of younger/older versions of Kalenz, Chantal, and Deoran appear
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1310
msgid ""
"I know who you are, Delfador of Alduin. But how well do you know yourselves?"
msgstr "我知道你是谁，奥渡因的德法多。但你们又对自己了解几分？"

#. [unit]: id=deoran_mirror
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1351
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:78
msgid "Deoran"
msgstr "德欧兰"

#. [message]
#. referencing the mirror image of Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1367
msgid "Deoran, is that... you? You look so much younger."
msgstr "德欧兰，那是……你吗？你看起来年轻了好多。"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1371
msgid "What’s going on?! Kalenz, is this normal?"
msgstr "发生什么事了？！卡雷兹，这是正常的吗？"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1397
msgid "Defeat all enemies"
msgstr "击败所有敌方首领"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#. if reduced to 0 hp, Delfador doesn't die. Instead, he's kicked out of the mirror world, and fails the scenario
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1402
msgid "Loss of Delfador"
msgstr "德法多死亡"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1414
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this strange world, fate guides every strike. <i>(attacks never miss)</i>"
msgstr "在这片诡谲的天地中，命运指引着每一击。<i>（攻击必中）</i>"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]: id=always_hit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1440
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The mortal world beckons; tell me the rest of the prophecy when next we meet!"
msgstr "尘世在呼唤；待下次相逢，愿闻预言之其余篇章！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]: id=always_hit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1441
#, fuzzy
msgid "Elende, I hope you know what you’re doing. Good luck, the rest of you!"
msgstr "艾莲德，但愿知你所为。诸位，祝好运！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]: id=always_hit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1442
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Owww! Elende, it’s very rude to banish someone without their permission!"
msgstr "哎哟！艾莲德，未经允许就把人强行送走，未免太无礼了！"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just been reduced to 0hp, and been "kicked out" of Elenede's "mirror realm" or wherever she was giving the prophecy
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1450
msgid "Hey, stop—"
msgstr "嘿，停下——"

#. [time]: id=dawn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1468
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1976
msgid "Dawn"
msgstr "黎明"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has missed the ending of the prophecy, and the player loses the scenario
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1493
msgid "I didn’t get to finish hearing everything..."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. spoken by Elende (through Kalenz's mirror image), referencing Legend of Wesmere's invisibility potion and Landar
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1523
msgid ""
"Lich’s eye and brother’s bone; what have you sacrificed to save your people, "
"Kalenz? Your greatest fear stands before you... ahead of you?"
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1527
#, fuzzy
msgid "That was long ago, Elende! This is about the humans’ story, not mine."
msgstr "那是久远的往事了，艾莲德！这关乎人类的命运，并非我个人的故事。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. spoken by Elende (through Deoran's mirror image), referencing his exile. I intend "nation" more in the "people" sense than the "country" sense.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1564
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran the exile returns home; returns to a nation that scorned him, ignored "
"his counsel and cast him away. What will become of the life he has built "
"amongst Lintanir’s twilight eaves?"
msgstr ""
"被放逐的德欧兰终将归乡；归来面对的是一个曾鄙夷他、无视他谏言并将其驱逐的国"
"度。他在林塔尼尔暮色檐下所构筑的人生，又将何去何从？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1568
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I know my duty! A captain of Wesnoth will never entertain doubts of loyalty, "
"whether to his country or his King."
msgstr ""
"我知晓我的职责！一名韦诺的统帅，无论是对国家还是对君王，绝不会有动摇忠诚的念"
"头。"

#. [message]
#. spoken by Elende (through Chantal's mirror image), referencing Cleodil's historic death and foreshadowing Deoran's upcoming death
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1581
msgid "Chantal—"
msgstr "香黛尔——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1585
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I already know what you’re going to say Elende! Don’t you dare; I will when "
"I’m ready."
msgstr "我早已知晓你待言何辞，艾莲德！休要逼我；待我时机成熟，自会开口。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1591
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Then you may soon understand some measure of your great-grandfather’s bygone "
"sorrows..."
msgstr "届时，你或能将你曾祖父昔日之哀伤，略窥一二……"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1670
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1921
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1928
msgid "Elende"
msgstr "艾莲德"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. Elende reaveals that she's the one who gave the weird prophecy thing to Delfador at Alduin, even though she wasn't physically there
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1673
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And what of the fire mage? Young but ambitious, brilliant yet foolish. It "
"has been many moons since I spoke to you at Alduin."
msgstr ""
"那位火焰法师又作何感想？年少却志存高远，天赋卓绝却未免鲁莽。自奥渡因一别，已"
"历数载寒暑，今始与君再会。"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1677
msgid ""
"That was you, back at graduation? I knew I heard a voice! Master Leollyn "
"thought I was going crazy..."
msgstr ""
"那就是你，在毕业典礼上？我就说曾听过那个声音！利欧林大师还以为我疯了呢……"

#. [event]
#. [event]: type=Delfador L4, id=delfador_mirror4
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1682
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1819
msgid ""
"Spend 4 XP to gain flight and the skirmisher ability until the start of your "
"next turn or until cancelled."
msgstr "花费4经验以获得飞行和散兵能力，直到你的下一个回合开始或直到被取消。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. pale spy meaning Asheviere. Referencing Asheviere resolving to kill Garard, and working with orcs to arrange the events of the next two scenarios
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1712
msgid ""
"I see secrets in the dark; a pale spy slips their bonds. A death, a "
"deceiver. Ringed swords, cold blood, false friends."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. referencing Delfador's adventures in scenarios 8-10, where he works with (or kills) poachers to fight saurians, then fights undead and a ghost given the appearance of a living drake.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1774
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The dark swamp looms. Purses and poachers, mirror and smoke. A figure of "
"shadow cloaked in the spirits of the dead. Battles won while wars are lost."
msgstr ""
"阴霾的沼泽 looming 在前方。钱袋与盗猎者，明镜与烟云。一道被亡灵英魂裹挟的阴影"
"之影。战局虽胜，却已输掉战争。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1781
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Spend 16 XP to disallow magical attacks in a 3-hex radius, until cancelled."
msgstr "消耗 16 点经验值，在 3 格范围内禁止魔法攻击，直至效果被取消。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. referencing the civil war when Asheviere takes power
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1806
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Brother against brother, father against child. From the barren throne will "
"rise an angel of ashes; both great and terrible alike. The delicate balance "
"of mankind will be broken, and flames shall blaze anew across the embers of "
"Haldric’s people."
msgstr ""
"手足相残，父弑其子。从荒废的王座之上，将升起一位灰烬天使；伟大而可怖，势均力"
"敌。人类微妙的平衡将被打破，赫德里克子民余烬之上，烈火将再度熊熊燃起。"

# Translated by openrouter with model z-ai/glm-4.5-air:free.
#. [event]: type=Delfador L4, id=delfador_mirror4
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1817
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Spend 48 XP to grant yourself and all allies double movement and a second "
"attack this turn. When this turn ends, affected units become slowed."
msgstr ""
"本回合内消耗**48点经验值**，使所有友军单位获得**双倍移动力**和**额外攻击**能"
"力。\n"
"当回合结束后，所有受此效果影响的单位将进入**减速**状态。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. referncing the future events of HttT; Konrad and Li'Sar retriving the sceptre of fire
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1910
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Black soot rains over Weldyn. The line of kings sundered; the ruby of the "
"wesfolk restored. The nameless son and the ashen daughter."
msgstr ""
"黑尘如雨倾落韦诺。王者之线已然断绝；韦诺族的红宝石重归其位。无名之子与灰烬之"
"女。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. referencing Delfador's choice in S10x
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1924
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But this fate is not the only path. Mage of Alduin, you stand at a knot in "
"the strands, a nexus of the shards. For one brief moment, you will possess "
"the power to alter the currents of time; to rewrite the future that is "
"written."
msgstr ""
"但此宿命并非唯一的道路。奥渡因的法师，你正伫立于丝缕交织的节点，立于万千碎片"
"的交汇之处。仅在一瞬之间，你将掌握扭转时光洪流、重写既定未来的权能。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. referencing Delfador's choice in S10x. He can either listen to a drunk Garard and kill Garard's brother Arand based on false reports of a betrayal, or refuse, stay with Garard, and find out more about Arand before attacking
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1931
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When that moment comes, remember... endeavor to bestow not destruction with "
"that fire that you possess, but the gleaming light of truth instead. Quench "
"the flames of fear before all your world is consumed."
msgstr ""
"当那一刻来临时，切记……莫要用你手中那圣火权杖燃起的烈焰去招致毁灭，而应施以真"
"理那光辉之光。在恐惧的烈焰吞噬世间万物之前，务必将其浇熄。"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1935
msgid "But, what? I don’t understa—"
msgstr "但是，什么？！我还不明——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador previously said "But, what? I don’t understa—", but has now been kicked out of Elende's 'mirror world' and is back in the normal world. The scenario is over.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:1999
#, fuzzy
msgid "—nd what you’re saying..."
msgstr "——你所说的……"

#. [scenario]: id=05_The_Deceiver
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:11
msgid "The Deceiver"
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:21
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador and his companions departed the mirror grove in hushed silence. The "
"Sylph’s words weighed heavily on each of their minds."
msgstr ""
"德法多与他的同伴们悄然离开了镜之丛林。风仙子的话语重若千钧，压在每个人的心"
"头。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:24
msgid ""
"After lengthy deliberation, and much to Chantal’s displeasure, Delfador and "
"Deoran resolved to continue on with their mission. Exiting the forest after "
"several days’ westward travel, they soon sighted the banners of the king’s "
"army."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Orcish Crossbowman, id=Shogro
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:50
#, fuzzy
msgid "Shogro"
msgstr "什格罗"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Khovak
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:68
msgid "Khovak"
msgstr "阔瓦克"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:297
msgid "90 gold"
msgstr "90金币"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:297
#, fuzzy
msgid "These orcs were sitting on some gold! We can put it to better use."
msgstr "这些兽人正守着大量黄金！咱们不如取来，派上更好的用场。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:311
msgid "Captain Kestrel"
msgstr "茶隼队长"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:360
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran, are you sure you won’t reconsider staying in the Lintanir? What "
"Elende said..."
msgstr "德欧兰，你当真不再考虑留在林塔尼尔了吗？毕竟……艾莲德所言非虚……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:364
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My duty comes first, always. Would you truly want me any other way, Chantal?"
msgstr "职责为先，此理恒常。香黛尔，你真会希望我成为别样模样吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#. referencing the beginning of HttT, where Delfador and Konrad are staying with the elves
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:370
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran, it has been a pleasure to have you with us these years. And "
"Delfador, I hope to someday say the same of you as well. Elende seems to "
"think highly of you, and that means a great deal to me and my people.\n"
"\n"
"Should either of you ever find yourselves searching for a home away from "
"Wesnoth, you will always be welcome with us."
msgstr ""
"德欧兰，这些年有你相伴，实乃幸事。德法多大师，我也希望日后能对你们两人说同样"
"的话。艾莲德对你们评价极高，这对我和子民而言，意义非凡。\n"
"\n"
"日后若你们二位寻得韦诺之外的栖身之所，我们林塔尼尔的家园将永远向你们敞开。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:386
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hail! The fledgling war-mage returns. Welcome, Delfador... and Deoran. Tell "
"me, are the north-elves with us?"
msgstr ""
"参见！新生的战法师归来了。欢迎，德法多……还有德欧兰。告诉我，北方的精灵们与我"
"们并肩作战了吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:390
#, fuzzy
msgid "Deepest apologies my Lord, but they are not. Lintanir—"
msgstr "请恕我冒昧，陛下，事实并非如此。林塔尼尔——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:394
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I see. Unfortunate, but ultimately of no consequence. Victory is nearly won "
"even without their aid."
msgstr ""
"我明白了。虽令人遗憾，但最终无足轻重。即便没有他们的援助，胜利也唾手可得。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:399
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"See there: we’ve driven the Whitefang chieftain and the last of his guards "
"into this old hill fort."
msgstr "瞧，我们已将白牙氏族酋长及其最后几名护卫逼入这座古老的丘陵要塞之中。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:403
msgid ""
"The timing of your return couldn’t have been better, Delfador. General "
"Lionel and my brother Arand will press them from the front, while you sneak "
"in the back and roast their chief like a pig on a spit."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:407
msgid ""
"Without their chief the Whitefangs will dissolve into an infighting mass of "
"petty squabbles, and our— Wesnoth’s victory will be complete!"
msgstr ""
"没了酋长，白牙氏族必将分崩离析，陷入无休止的内斗，而我们——韦诺的胜利，终将圆"
"满！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:415
msgid "Defeat Khovak, the orcish warlord"
msgstr "击败兽人军阀阔瓦克"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:419
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:550
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:504
msgid "Death of Delfador or Deoran"
msgstr "德法多或德欧兰死亡"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:423
msgid "Death of Garard, Arand, Lionel, or Methor"
msgstr "伽拉德、阿兰德、莱昂内尔或梅瑟死亡"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:444
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Don’t rush the assault, Lionel — no need to waste good men. Take some time "
"to stage our forces outside their walls, then attack just before the second "
"dawn."
msgstr ""
"别急于发动攻势，莱昂内尔——不必白白牺牲优秀的将士。先花些时间将我们的部队在城"
"外集结部署，待到第二道曙光将至时，再发动进攻。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:448
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We have them right where we want them. Once our forces are assembled, I "
"shall join the battle personally and savor this victory up close."
msgstr ""
"“我们要的猎物已入瓮口。待我军集结完毕，我当亲临战场，近距离品味这来之不易的胜"
"果。”"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:452
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’m surprised the Whitefangs have been driven to the brink of defeat so "
"quickly. Chantal speaks of them as numerous and cunning... I wonder if "
"something is amiss."
msgstr ""
"我颇感讶异，白牙氏族的溃败竟来得如此迅猛。香黛尔曾言他们兵众狡黠……我不禁疑"
"心，其中恐有蹊跷。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:464
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An orcish shaman! On occasion I’ve known some of the other clans to use "
"their apprentices as warriors, but Clan Whitefang usually keeps theirs far "
"from the frontline."
msgstr ""
"一名兽人萨满！偶有听闻，其他氏族会将学徒派作战士，但白牙氏族向来不让其学徒涉"
"足前线。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:468
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What unusual magic! I don’t think I can tap into whatever fundamental forces "
"she was using, but now that I have her equipment I’ll bet I could figure out "
"how to imitate that draining attack... for our next battle, at least."
msgstr ""
"多么奇特的魔法！我想我无法直接引导她所运用那股本源之力，但如今我已掌握了她的"
"装备，我敢打赌——至少在下一次战役中，定能破解其夺命攻击的奥秘，并将其化为己"
"用。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:494
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I have still not recruited or recalled any soldiers! That orcish shaman we "
"defeated was standing on a keep. We should seize it and recruit our army "
"before we attack the orcs’ main camp."
msgstr ""
"我竟尚未招募或召回任何士兵！我们之前击败的那名兽人萨满正站在一座要塞上。我们"
"应当夺取此地，在进攻兽人主营之前先整军备旅。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:518
#, fuzzy
msgid "There’s more of them coming from the north! Should we go attack?"
msgstr "北方还有更多敌军逼近！我们要主动出击吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Khovak
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:522
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stay in our fort, worm! Stick to the plan."
msgstr "留在我们的堡垒里，蠕虫！死守计划！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. "trog" is a made-up slur referring to an orc
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:535
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re squatting in my summer home, trogs! No more raids for you; no more "
"pillage and plunder. Last chance to surrender!"
msgstr ""
"你们竟敢蹲伏在我的夏日行宫，侏儒杂种！别再做劫掠勾当了，别再肆行烧杀抢掠！这"
"是你们最后投降的机会！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:539
msgid "Up yours, pink-skin!"
msgstr "去你妈的，粉皮崽子！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador is telling his master Methor about the adventures he had in the last 2 scenarios
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:564
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hello there, master, it’s nice to see you again! You’ll never believe the "
"adventures I’ve had. Did you know there’s an elvish prophecy about me?!"
msgstr ""
"大师，久违了！能再次见到您，学生德法多倍感荣幸。您绝对无法相信，我近来经历了"
"何等奇遇。甚至，您可知晓有一则精灵预言，竟将主角定为我德法多本人？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:568
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(smiling) Delfador, don’t make me regret teaching you that psychedelic "
"spell! I’m just glad you’ve made it back safe and sound."
msgstr ""
"(面带微笑) 德法多，可别让我后悔曾教你那道幻彩法术！我只庆幸你平安归来。"

#. [message]: speaker=Shogro
#. the whitefangs orcs are luring Garard into overextending. Shogro is bait, and has just died
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:582
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stinking Ushka’e! This was a terrible plan..."
msgstr "卑鄙的乌什卡尔！这真是个糟糕的计策……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Khovak
#. the whitefangs orcs are luring Garard into overextending. Khovak is bait, and has just died
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:607
#, fuzzy
msgid "Human dogs! You’ve just sealed your deaths..."
msgstr "人类犬类！你们刚刚亲手为自已判了死罪……"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:624
msgid "Run for the hills!"
msgstr "快撤往山岭！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:639
#, fuzzy
msgid "Yes! Did I do well, Your Majesty?"
msgstr "是！陛下，我表现得可还够格？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard thinks he's won, even though he hasn't
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:644
#, fuzzy
msgid "Indeed you did. Fantastic battle, everyone, the orcs are broken!"
msgstr "确实如此。精彩绝伦的一战，各位！兽人已然溃不成军！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:652
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Footmen — down into the fort’s dungeons! Flush out any stragglers and "
"complete our victory."
msgstr "步兵——进入要塞的牢狱！肃清任何漏网之鱼，以确证我军的胜利。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard thinks he's won, even though he hasn't. "Wold" means "a piece of high, open, uncultivated land or moor."
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:696
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hah! I think “Garard’s Wold” will make a good name for the new province... "
"or perhaps “Garard’s Triumph”? What do you think, Lionel?"
msgstr ""
"哈！我想“伽拉德的沃德高地”（Garard's Wold）作新行省的名字挺不错……或者改成“伽"
"拉德的凯旋”？莱昂内尔，你觉得如何？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:701
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, something’s wrong. The orc leader we killed... isn’t the Whitefang "
"chief."
msgstr "德法多大师，有些不对劲。我们击杀的兽人首领……并非白牙氏族的酋长。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:705
#, fuzzy
msgid "What? How can you tell?"
msgstr "什么？你是如何察觉的？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:709
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I met Clan Whitefang’s leaders around a year ago, when Lintanir negotiated a "
"treaty. This orc’s face is narrower than I remember, and his helmet doesn’t "
"have the right war-paint. Delfador, I think we’ve been tricked!"
msgstr ""
"我与白牙氏族的领袖们约莫一年前相识，当时是林塔尼尔正在协商条约之际。眼前这兽"
"人的面庞比我记忆中更为狭窄，且其头盔上并未绘有正确的战纹。德法多，我想我们遭"
"人算计了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:756
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Are you even trying to fight, Delfador!? I should have known a mage would "
"never have the stomach for true battle; get back to Alduin where you belong!"
msgstr ""
"你当真在战斗吗，德法多大师？我早该料到，法师终究缺乏投身真正战场的胆魄；滚回"
"奥渡因去吧，那里才是你该待的地方！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=06_Ring_of_Swords
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:12
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ring of Swords"
msgstr "剑环"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Ghazgir
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:51
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ghazgir"
msgstr "古兹吉尔"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Direwolf Rider, id=Mukhu
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:68
#, fuzzy
msgid "Muhku"
msgstr "唔呼库"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Leader, id=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:89
msgid "Irbirch"
msgstr "伊尔比奇"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Orcish Leader, id=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:96
#, fuzzy
msgid "Blackcrest Orcs"
msgstr "黑脊兽人"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Saurian Flanker, id=Ssisaix
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:106
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ssisaix"
msgstr "西沙伊克"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Saurian Flanker, id=Ssisaix
#. [side]: type=Saurian Javelineer, id=Xairr
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:112
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:128
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:79
#, fuzzy
msgid "Blackcrest Saurians"
msgstr "黑鳍蜥蜴人"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Saurian Javelineer, id=Xairr
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:122
#, fuzzy
msgid "Xairr"
msgstr "夏伊尔"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:374
msgid "Chief Ushka'e"
msgstr "乌什卡尔酋长"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#. this is the whitefang chief. He's happy that Garard has walked into his trap
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:380
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You see? What did I tell you! Their king is nothing but a feeble-minded "
"goblin runt, who does exactly what I want. The trap is sprung! Now we crush "
"them."
msgstr ""
"看到了吗？我早就说过！他们的国王不过是个心智迟钝的矮小妖物，乖乖地照着我的意"
"愿行动。陷阱已经成功触发！现在，让我们将他们碾碎！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. Irbirch is a representative of clan blackcrest, now (tenuously) allied with whitefang. The "spy" references Asheviere (probably; might be an agent of Iliah-Malal instead), who came up with the plan and told it to the orcs
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:402
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Bwahaha, when did you Whitefangs become so weak as to follow the ploy of a "
"spy? Blackcrest warriors would never have let humans advance so far into our "
"lands!"
msgstr ""
"哈哈哈！你们白牙氏族的家伙们是何时变得如此孱弱，竟会中一个间谍的计谋？若是黑"
"牙氏族的战士们在此，绝不可能容许人类如此深入我们的土地！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#. referencing clan blackcrest's saurian allies.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:407
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your “warriors” only survive by cowering behind your slimy lizard allies! "
"But since Clan Blackcrest has begged so-like trembling goblins, Clan "
"Whitefang will agree to work together."
msgstr ""
"你们的“勇士”不过是蜷缩在你们那些黏糊糊的蜥蜴盟友身后苟延残喘罢了！不过，既然"
"黑牙氏族像发抖的小鬼一样苦苦哀求，白牙氏族便同意联手。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. neither side has actually offered to work together. Subversive messengers poised as members of each clan and manipulated them into working together against Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:412
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Since WE begged!? YOU invited US here; your messenger was quaking in his "
"boots when he groveled before Chief Ghuvog asking for help!"
msgstr ""
"竟敢让我们乞求？分明是你们邀请我们来此！你们派去恳求古沃格酋长援助的信使，当"
"时可是吓得双腿发软、伏地求饶啊！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:416
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What are you talking abo— Oh forget it, just make sure your clan does its "
"job! No human leaves this valley alive!"
msgstr ""
"你在胡言乱语什——哦算了，只要你们氏族完成分内事就行！绝不允许人类活着走出这片"
"山谷！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:436
msgid "Bazur"
msgstr "巴祖尔"

#. [message]: speaker=Bazur
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:444
msgid "Lousy chief! Lousy plan! Next time I’m doing this on my own terms!"
msgstr "窝囊的酋长！烂透的计划！下次这事儿，我按自己的规矩来！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard has just realized he's surrounded
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:462
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What devilry is this? How did they sneak in behind us. I’m separated from my "
"generals and most of my soldiers..."
msgstr ""
"这究竟是什么妖术？他们究竟是如何潜行到我军身后的？我已与我的将领们以及大部分"
"士兵失去了联系……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:466
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Foul orcs, come at me then! If this is where I am to fall, I shall make such "
"a stand as to stir the gods themselves to tears!"
msgstr ""
"卑鄙的兽人，那就来吧！若我今日必死于此，定当力战至死，令众神亦为之动容落泪！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. Asheviere is next to Irbirch. The player is led to think she's been captured, but it's possible she actually went of her own free will to escape Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:476
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Nice speech! I wonder what your wife thinks of it? Don’t worry, we’ll have "
"plenty of fun with her, <b><i>and</i></b> your unborn heir. Haw, haw, haw!"
msgstr ""
"好一场精彩的演说！不知尊夫人对此有何感想？别担心，我们会让她，<b><i>以及</"
"i></b>你那未出世的血脉，好好享受“乐趣”的。哈，哈，哈！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:500
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(aghast) That’s— They’ve captured the queen! Asheviere’s no warrior, and "
"fragile with pregnancy. We have to rescue her!"
msgstr ""
"（骇然）这——他们劫持了王后！艾什薇尔并非战士，且身怀六甲，体弱不堪。我们必须"
"救她出来！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:504
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Surrounded and absent the queen; this is a disaster! Quick, we must rally "
"what’s left of the crown’s infantry. Send a detachment to rescue Queen "
"Asheviere, and have the rest protect King Garard until Lionel and Arand can "
"break through to us!"
msgstr ""
"王后失位，我们已陷重围，此乃灭顶之灾！速将王庭步兵残部重整！即刻派遣一支分遣"
"队去营救王后艾什薇尔，其余部队务必守护国王伽拉德，直至莱昂内尔与阿兰德杀出重"
"围，与我们会合！"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:508
msgid "I won’t let you down! For Wesnoth!"
msgstr "我绝不会辜负你们！为了韦诺！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:515
msgid "Fail to rescue Asheviere before turns run out"
msgstr "回合耗尽之前没能救出艾什薇尔"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:518
msgid "Defeat Irbirch to recapture Asheviere, then survive until turns run out"
msgstr "击败伊尔比奇以夺回艾什薇尔，随后坚持至回合耗尽"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:525
msgid "Survive until turns run out"
msgstr "生存至回合耗尽"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:554
msgid "Death of Garard, Asheviere, or Methor"
msgstr "伽拉德，艾什薇尔或梅瑟死亡"

#. [message]: speaker=Ssisaix
#. the player (and Garard) is still alive. The orcs and saurians expected them to die by now
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:615
msgid "They ssstill sssurvive! Thisss was not the plan!"
msgstr "他们还或者嘶嘶！计划不是这样的嘶嘶！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:619
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Then send in more warriors and finish them off, you worthless Blackcrest "
"lizards! This is <b>our</b> homeland; our ranks swell by the hour, while "
"these humans dwindle every moment."
msgstr ""
"那就再派些战士过来，把这些该死的黑脊蜥蜴彻底宰了！这是<b>我们</b>的家园！我们"
"的兵源每时都在扩充，而那些人族却在时刻衰亡！"

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:624
msgid ""
"Useless lizards! Can’t even keep themselves alive, much less win a war. Send "
"in more orcs! This is <b>our</b> homeland; our ranks swell by the hour, "
"while these humans dwindle every moment."
msgstr ""
"没用的蜥蜴！连自己的命都保不住，更别提打赢这场战争了。继续派兽人！这可是<b>我"
"们</b>的家园；我们的兵力每小时都在壮大，而这些人类每一刻都在不断消亡。"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:637
msgid "They’re being reinforced!"
msgstr "他们正在增援！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:676
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This alliance between races is a great ill fortune! I’ve oft known orcs to "
"recruit trolls, but seldom saurians. And with these three factions fighting "
"together, soon all the warlords will hear of their prowess."
msgstr ""
"种族间的这种结盟实乃大不幸！我常闻兽人征召巨魔，却极少听闻蜥蜴人。而这三大势"
"力若联手作战，不久后，所有军阀皆将闻知他们的赫赫战功。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:680
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It takes a great show of strength to unite the fractious orcs, but after "
"this disaster countless more will surely flock to the Blackcrest and "
"Whitefang banners. Orcs follow might above all else, even clan blood."
msgstr ""
"要团结这些桀骜不驯的兽人，非得展现出压倒性的力量不可。但这场灾难之后，必将有"
"无数兽人蜂拥至黑冠与白牙的旗下。对兽人而言，唯有力量才是至高无上的信条，甚至"
"胜过氏族的血缘。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:684
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Utter madness, all of this! The orcish clans are a hornet’s nest that should "
"never have been kicked. Pillagers and raids we can deal with, but total war "
"is something else entirely."
msgstr ""
"简直是彻头彻尾的疯狂！兽人各部族本是绝不可轻易撼动的马蜂窝。打劫与突袭，我们"
"尚且能够应对，但全面战争……那完全是另一码事。"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:688
msgid "Quiet, both of you! If I wanted your advice I would have asked for it!"
msgstr "你们两个，都给我闭嘴！若我需要你们的建议，我自会开口相求！"

#. [message]: speaker=Ushka'e
#. the player has just attacked the whitefang chief. He then flees
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:700
msgid "Worthless humans! You’ll never defeat me, or clan Whitefang!"
msgstr "卑劣的人类！你们永远无法击败我，也无法征服白牙氏族！"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:706
msgid "Coward! Stand and fight!"
msgstr "懦夫！站住迎战！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ssisaix
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:721
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They sssneak off to the northeassst, towardsss their queen! Ssshould I "
"pursssue?"
msgstr "他们正悄然潜行向东北方，直扑她们的王后！我是否要追击？"

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:725
msgid "Finish off their king, lizard! I’ll handle things here."
msgstr "宰了他们的国王，蜥蜴！这儿的事我来处理。"

#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:737
msgid "Come to ransom back your queen? Too bad, she’s mine!"
msgstr "来赎你的王后？真可惜，她归我了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:741
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Maybe once she pops out her kid you can pay me double for both! Haw, haw, "
"haw."
msgstr "说不定等这位太太把孩子生下来，你就能付我双倍的双份报酬啦！哈，哈，哈。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Irbirch
#. a representative of clan blackcrest has died
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:753
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Great Chief Ghuvog will avenge me! Clan Blackcrest will never rest.. until "
"Wesnoth is... razed to... ash..."
msgstr "伟大的古沃格酋长必将为我复仇！黑牙氏族永不安息……直到韦诺……化为……灰烬……"

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#. Asheviere tries to say something, but gets interrupted
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:766
msgid "Thank yo—"
msgstr "谢——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. both Deoran and Garard talk over Asheviere. She doesn't get any agency of her own, even from Deoran (who generally stands up for her)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:771
#, fuzzy
msgid "Not now, milady! We have to get you out of here!"
msgstr "“夫人，现在不是时候！我们得立刻带您离开这儿！”"

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#. asheviere tries to say something, but gets interrupted
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:781
msgid "Garard, I—"
msgstr "伽拉德，我——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. both Deoran and Garard talk over Asheviere. She doesn't get any agency of her own, even from Deoran (who generally stands up for her)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:786
#, fuzzy
msgid "Not now, woman! I have a battle to fight!"
msgstr "别现在，女人！我正要去迎战！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghazgir
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:799
#, fuzzy
msgid "I’m not dying! Just... need a moment..."
msgstr "我才不会死！只是……需要片刻……"

#. [message]: speaker=Mukhu
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:806
msgid "Nooo! Help meeee!"
msgstr "不——！救救我——！"

#. [message]: speaker=Xairr
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:813
msgid "Ssssuch ssssskill!"
msgstr "好精湛的技艺嘶嘶！"

#. [message]: speaker=Ssisaix
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:820
msgid "Cursessss, I am sssslain!"
msgstr "该死嘶嘶，我被杀了嘶嘶！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#. Lionel appears with reinforcments to help Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:868
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Rally behind me, men! We swore our oaths, now we do our duty. Fight, fight "
"through to the king!"
msgstr ""
"集结于我身后，勇士们！我们曾立下誓言，如今正是履行使命之时。杀！杀向君王！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. the player has survived, but failed ot rescue the queen
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:887
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But the queen! If we leave her in the hands of the orcs she’ll surely be "
"tortured and killed!"
msgstr "但王后！若我们将她留予兽人，她必遭酷刑，最终惨死！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:891
#, fuzzy
msgid "I’m sorry, there’s no time! We have to get the king out of here!"
msgstr "抱歉，没时间了！我们必须立刻护送国王离开此地！"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:912
msgid "Sir, look out!"
msgstr "大人，小心！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:927
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1395
#, fuzzy
msgid "<b><i>NNnrgh!</i></b>"
msgstr "<b><i>呃——啊！</i></b>"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#. Lionel has appeared with reinforcments to help Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:946
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By the Sceptre, I got here just in time! They caught us completely by "
"surprise. We’re holding a corridor but I don’t know for how long — we’ve got "
"to get you back to Fort Garard, sir."
msgstr ""
"以圣火权杖之名，我总算及时赶到了！他们完全出其不意地袭击了我们。我们勉强守住"
"了一条走廊，但不知能坚持多久——先生，我们必须带您立刻返回加拉德堡！"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:950
msgid "Lionel! I’d almost feared this was the end."
msgstr "莱昂内尔！我几乎以为这就到了尽头。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:963
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But how did this disaster happen? We were on the eve of victory! Did someone "
"betray our plans to the enemy? Or am I really just that predictable!?"
msgstr ""
"但这灾难究竟是如何发生的？我们明明已站在胜利的门槛之上！难道有人向敌人泄露了"
"我们的计划？还是说……我竟真的如此不堪一击，如此容易被人看穿？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:967
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Couldn’t tell you, m’lord. But there’ll be time to talk later. It looks like "
"this war is going to last a lot longer than we’d planned..."
msgstr ""
"“恕难相告，大人。但稍后自当细谈。看来这场战争，将比我们预想的更加漫长……”"

#. [scenario]: id=07_The_Great_River
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:28
msgid "The Great River"
msgstr "泰河"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:53
msgid "Part II"
msgstr "第二部"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:59
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The entry of Clan Blackcrest into the war opens up a new front further west, "
"demanding swift response. Wesnoth fully mobilizes, and a series of bloody "
"battles at the Ford of Abez end in deadlock for both sides. The ford is "
"heavily fortified, and river commerce grinds to a halt. Many years pass, "
"with neither side able to gain an advantage."
msgstr ""
"黑牙氏族的介入开启了西部战线的新战场，迫使韦诺王国必须迅速作出反应。全境动员"
"之下，一系列在雅碧滩的惨烈战役使得双方陷入僵持。此地要塞森严，河流贸易彻底停"
"滞。岁月流转，双方均未能占据上风。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:63
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Meanwhile, Asheviere gives birth to a healthy baby boy — the Crown Prince "
"Eldred. Under heavy pressure from both parents and via the tutelage of "
"General Lionel, Eldred rapidly matures into a princeling soldier. Prince "
"Arand takes Eldred under his wing, and working in tandem the uncle and "
"nephew are able to stabilize the eastern front around Fort Garard. Whitefang "
"orcs still firmly hold the hills, but limited settlement begins."
msgstr ""
"与此同时，艾什薇尔诞下一名健康的男婴——即未来的王储，埃雷德王子。在双亲的巨大"
"压力以及莱昂内尔将军的悉心调教下，埃雷德迅速成长为一名骁勇的王子兼士兵。阿兰"
"德亲王将埃雷德收入羽翼之下，叔侄二人通力合作，成功稳定了伽拉德要塞周边的东部"
"战线。尽管白牙氏族的兽人仍牢牢占据着山丘要地，但有限的定居点已开始在那片土地"
"生根发芽。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:67
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador grows older, wiser, and significantly more powerful. He makes a "
"name for himself as the king’s premier war-mage, and quickly gains a "
"reputation as a ferocious fighter. His bold maneuvers break through orcish "
"lines several times at the Ford of Abez, but continually become stymied by "
"saurian reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"德法多日益年长，智慧与力量皆臻化境。他以此名震朝野，成为国王麾下首席战法师，"
"并迅速以骁勇无畏的战士之名传颂四方。在雅碧滩，他屡以大胆奇策撕裂兽人防线，却"
"总受制于蜥蜴人的源源增援，功败垂成。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:71
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As Wesnoth’s casualties continue to mount, and with no end in sight, "
"Delfador decides to take matters into his own hands. The war-mage prepares a "
"force of mercenary northmen to sneak behind enemy lines and determine the "
"nature of Clan Blackcrest’s orc-saurian alliance..."
msgstr ""
"随着韦诺的伤亡不断攀升，而胜利似乎遥遥无期，德法多决定亲自出马。这位战争法师"
"集结了一支北方雇佣军，潜入敌后，以探查黑冠氏族与蜥蜴人联盟的真相……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:89
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:61
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:33
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:31
#, fuzzy
msgid "Delfador’s Hirelings"
msgstr "德法多的雇佣兵"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
