#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:1058
msgid "Reselecting Spells:"
msgstr "重新选择法术："

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:1059
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Because the scenario’s objectives have significantly changed (in a way you "
"couldn’t have anticipated at the scenario’s start), you now have the option "
"to change your spells."
msgstr ""
"因战役目标已发生剧变（其变化方式远超战役开局时的预料），现你可选择更换法术。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:1071
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We must defeat these saurians and escape before nightfall, or the main "
"orcish camp will wake and be upon us!"
