# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:355
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The seven saurian matriarchs lie somewhere in this swamp. With most of their "
"warriors away at war, they will be vulnerable."
msgstr ""
"七位蜥蜴人母王后正身处这恐惧沼泽的某处。因她们麾下大军已开赴战场，此刻正是它"
"们最为脆弱之时。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:359
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Blackcrests have good reason to fight, but none of this should concern "
"saurians — they’re not usually invaders. I need to figure out what’s going "
"on with this alliance and put an end to it."
msgstr ""
"黑冠氏族有充分的理由开战，但这一切本不该由蜥蜴人操心——他们向来不喜侵略。我必"
"须查清这联盟究竟因何而起，并彻底将其终结。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. in this string, $companion_name is female (probably "Lynyan")
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:365
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"female^That is, if we can find their camps. This ruined place was once a "
"great city of their kind — even what little remains is too vast for us to "
"scour it all. This is where you said your guides would meet us, "
"$companion_name?"
msgstr ""
"女声^只要我们能找到他们的营地。此处曾是他们种族的一座宏伟都市——即便仅存之残"
"骸，其规模亦大得令我等无法尽数搜罗。此乃你说你的向导将与我们会合之"
"处，$companion_name？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. in this string, $companion_name is male
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:371
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That is, if we can find their camps. This ruined place was once a great city "
"of their kind — even what little remains is too vast for us to scour it all. "
"This is where you said your guides would meet us, $companion_name?"
msgstr ""
"这还得看我们能否找到他们的营地。此地昔日乃是同类所建之辉煌之城——即便仅存之残"
"垣断壁，亦浩瀚无边，非我等之力所能尽搜。此即你言，你的向导将在此与我们会合之"
"地，$companion_name？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:376
#, fuzzy
msgid "You’re almost there! Jus’ a lil bit further... almost..."
msgstr "你已经快到了！再走一点点……就要……到了……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:390
#, fuzzy
msgid "Rendezvous with your companion’s guides"
msgstr "与盟友的向导会合"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:443
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hey, what—"
msgstr "嘿，什么——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]: id=activate_poachers
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:447
#, fuzzy
msgid "Gonnin"
msgstr "贡宁"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]: id=activate_poachers
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:452
#, fuzzy
msgid "Milyn"
msgstr "米琳"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]: id=activate_poachers
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:457
#, fuzzy
msgid "Barin"
msgstr "巴林"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Barin
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:463
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Well well, look what the cat dragged in. You’re a little far from home, "
"scholar!"
msgstr "哎呀呀，瞧瞧这是谁？把你这只老猫拖来了。学者，你离家可不近啊！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Barin
#. "protection" is a reference to a "protection racket", where organized crime will extort money from victims. Barin isn't actually proposing a protection racket - he's genuinely offering to help Delfador - but it's meant to sound ambiguous and suspicious
#. this is also a reference to a similar scenario in Delfador's Memoirs, where bandits actually are trying to rob you (unless you're on Easy, in which case they join you)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:469
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There’s lizards out here... and robbers too. T’would be a shame if something "
"happened to you. Maybe you oughta have our protection — for a price."
msgstr ""
"外面有蜥蜴人，也有强盗。若阁下出了什么意外，那未免太可惜了。或许……您该寻求我"
"们的庇护——当然，是另收一笔费用的。"

#. [option]
#. $fee is very likely between 24 and 100
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:484
msgid "Pay $fee gold (learn to recruit Poachers)"
msgstr "支付 $fee 金币（学会征募偷猎者）"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:490
msgid "Attack"
msgstr "攻击"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Barin
#. in this string, $companion_name is female (probably "Lynyan")
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:516
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"female^Great! Rest easy now that you’ve hired us; we’ll guide you ’round the "
"swamp and make sure nothin’ happens to you or the rest of your coin! "
"$companion_name said yer looking for them lizards, yeah?"
msgstr ""
"女^太好了！既然您已雇佣了我们，便请放心安歇。待我们护送您穿过恐惧沼泽，定保您"
"与诸位同伴安然无恙！听$companion_name 说，您正在寻那些蜥蜴人，可没错？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Barin
#. in this string, $companion_name is male
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:522
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Great! Rest easy now that you’ve hired us; we’ll guide you ’round the swamp "
"and make sure nothin’ happens to you or the rest of your coin! "
"$companion_name said yer looking for them lizards, yeah?"
msgstr ""
"太好了！既已雇佣我们，您便且放宽心。我们将引领您穿越这片恐惧沼泽，确保您与同"
"伴——您那些“宝贝”金币——毫发无损！刚才听您那伙伴说（那位男士），您是在寻那些蜥"
"蜴人，对吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Barin
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:538
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...what, you didn’t think we was trying to rob something, did ye? Naw, I’m "
"your guide. I’d never hurt a friend of $companion_name’s."
msgstr ""
"……怎么，你们没想过我们会来打劫什么？别逗了，我是你们的向导。我绝不会伤害朋友 "
"$companion_name 的人。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:545
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Poachers are general-purpose nighttime archers, with numerous-but-weak "
"ranged strikes and unusually good defense in swamps."
msgstr ""
"盗贼是通用的夜间弓兵，拥有大量但微弱的远程攻击，且在沼泽中防御力异常出色。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:570
#, fuzzy
msgid "Insolent fools, I am no sickly scribe, easy pickings for the robber!"
msgstr "无耻之徒！我绝非那孱弱易欺的书吏，岂容强盗随意宰割！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Barin
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:574
#, fuzzy
msgid "Whoah, hey uh, what’s going on?"
msgstr "哇哦，嘿，呃，这是怎么回事？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:578
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You bandits trifle with an archmage of Wesnoth, famed and powerful. Step "
"forth and meet your doom!"
msgstr ""
"你们这些强盗竟敢戏弄韦诺王国那位名震天下、法力无边的传奇大法师？站出来吧，迎"
"接你们的末日！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:599
msgid "Defeat the bandits"
msgstr "击败土匪"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:620
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ughhh..."
msgstr "呃……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:628
#, fuzzy
msgid "I’m gettin’ out o’ here!"
msgstr "我得赶紧离开这儿！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:637
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Serves them right, preying on innocent travelers... Now, where’s these "
"guides of yours we’re going to meet?"
msgstr "他们自食恶果，竟敢劫掠无辜旅人……好了，我们要会见的向导们究竟在哪儿？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:641
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Umm... you know what, I’m thinkin’ we’re better off hunting them saurians "
"all on our lonesomes instead. I’m still gettin’ paid after all this, right?"
msgstr ""
"嗯……这么说吧，我觉得咱们不如各自单独行动，去猎杀那些蜥蜴人算了。不管发生什"
"么，我都能拿到报酬，对吧？"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:655
msgid "Defeat three of the seven saurian leaders"
msgstr "击败七个蜥蜴人首领中的三个"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:672
msgid "(3 remaining)"
msgstr "（剩下3个）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:674
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Surprise attack: The saurians will not spot you until you approach within 4 "
"hexes of a matriarch."
msgstr "突袭：蜥蜴人只有在您逼近母蜥蜴至 4 格范围内时才会发现您。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:695
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That saurian has different markings than the others I’ve seen, and is "
"somewhat smaller. A juvenile or invalid, perhaps?"
msgstr ""
"那条蜥蜴人的纹饰与我所见过的其他同类迥异，身形也略显矮小。莫非是幼崽，或是体"
"弱之人？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. delfador has just attacked an unarmed saurian
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:703
#, fuzzy
msgid "The monssstersss hunt usss for sssport! Flee, flee!"
msgstr "怪物们以猎杀我们为乐！快逃，快逃！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:707
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They really are unarmed juveniles! Hang on a minute, they’re not dangerous, "
"maybe we should just let them be."
msgstr ""
"他们竟真的是毫无武装的孩童！稍等片刻，看来并不可怕……或许，我们该放他们一马。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:730
#, fuzzy
msgid "We’re under assssault! Sssound the alarm and rally our warriorsss!"
msgstr "遭突袭了！速鸣警钟，集结我军勇士！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:734
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They’ve spotted us! The time for stealth is past; now come the fire and the "
"flame!"
msgstr "他们发现我们了！隐忍潜行之时已逝，此刻，烈火与烈焰将倾覆一切！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:757
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There are few villages to be found here, but look! We have stumbled upon an "
"oasis.\n"
"\n"
"Like villages, an oasis will heal anyone standing on it. Unlike villages, an "
"oasis provides neither income nor protection."
msgstr ""
"此地村落寥寥，但请看！我们竟偶然发现了一处绿洲。\n"
"\n"
"如同村落，凡伫立其上者皆可疗伤；但不同于村落，绿洲既不产粮，亦无屏障。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:787
#, fuzzy
msgid "Who are you! Why bring death into my homesss..."
msgstr "你是谁！为何将死亡带至我的家园……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:791
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I am Delfador, war-mage of Wesnoth! Abandon the Blackcrest orcs to death by "
"Wesnoth’s spears, or I will visit upon you the same destruction your allies "
"would bring to us!"
msgstr ""
"吾乃德法多大师，韦诺的战争法师！将那些黑 crest 兽人任由韦诺的长矛终结，否则，"
"我将让你们遭受的毁灭，正如你们那些盟友本欲加诸于我之身的灾厄！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:795
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But tribe Earth-Becomes-Clay mussst fight Wesssnoth! The Great One has "
"commanded us!"
msgstr "但“土化土块”部族必须向韦诺开战！那位伟大的存在已命令我们！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:799
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The “Great One”? I had thought you matriarchs led your tribe. Tell me, "
"elder, who is this of which you speak?"
msgstr ""
"“伟大者”？我以为是你们的女性族长统御着氏族。请告诉我，长者，您所提及的那位究"
"竟是何人？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:803
msgid ""
"We sssauriansss are finally united... the Great One makesss usss... "
"ssstrong..."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:809
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Alas, she has expired. Her wounds were too great. But we have learned much — "
"we must capture another matriarch to find out who this ’great one’ is."
msgstr ""
"唉，她已气绝。她的伤势太过深重。但我们收获颇丰——必须再擒获一位女族长，方能揭"
"晓这位“伟大者”究竟是何人。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:811
msgid "(2 remaining)"
msgstr "（剩下2个）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:828
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You are beaten, lizard! Your ’great one’ commands you to kill my people; "
"tell me who or what the ’great one’ is, and your life shall be spared."
msgstr ""
"你已败北，蜥蜴人！你那所谓的“至尊者”命令你屠杀我的子民。告诉我，这“至尊者”究"
"竟是谁，亦或为何物？若你如实相告，你的性命便可得免。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:832
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Curssse you! We are all nothing but wormsss before her... she will dessstroy "
"you in an inferno of flamesss!"
msgstr "诅咒你！在她面前，我们皆是……蠕虫……她必将以烈火之狱，将你彻底焚毁！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:850
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And I shall destroy YOU in an inferno of flames if you don’t tell me what I "
"want to know!"
msgstr "若你不肯说出我所想知的一切，我便让你陷入烈火炼狱之中，彻底毁灭！"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:862
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:780
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1371
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1862
msgid "fireball"
msgstr "火球"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:880
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Wait, what! I wasn’t actually going to— that wasn’t supposed to happen! "
"Where did that fireball come from!"
msgstr "且慢！这……我本无意如此——这不该发生啊！那火球究竟从何而来！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:884
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...it seems I’ve spent so much time building my power that I neglected the "
"finer arts of control. Methor would be ashamed... I must redouble my efforts."
msgstr ""
"……看来我倾注了太多精力去构建力量，反倒荒废了更为精微的掌控之道。梅瑟若见之，"
"定会深感羞耻……我务必加倍努力。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:905
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...decades ago, an elvish seer told me about <i>“the dark swamp”</i>, and "
"that I must <i>“endeavour to bestow not destruction with that fire that I "
"possess, but the gleaming light of truth instead.”</i> Surely this was not "
"the event that she referred to?"
msgstr ""
"……数十载前，一位精灵先知曾对我提及那片“黑暗沼泽”，并告诫我务必“莫以我掌中之火"
"施以毁灭，而当以此火化作真理之璀璨光辉。”难道说的便是眼前这一幕吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:909
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Garard thinks little of such superstition, but I have done my best to follow "
"that cryptic advice. Yet I confess I understand precious little of what she "
"was trying to say. Why must seers always speak in riddles? It is hard to "
"think clearly, especially in times of crisis..."
msgstr ""
"伽拉德对这类迷信嗤之以鼻，但我已竭尽全力去遵循她那些 cryptic 的忠告。然而，我"
"坦白承认，对她试图传达的含义，我其实知之甚少。为何先知们总爱用谜语说话？在危"
"机时刻，想要保持清晰的思维尤为艰难……"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:912
msgid "(1 remaining)"
msgstr "（剩下1个）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:935
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Cease your fighting, matriarch, for you have been bested! Heed this warning: "
"answer my questions or be burned to ashes!"
msgstr "停下吧，女族长，你已败北！谨听此警示：答我之问，否则化为灰烬！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador was worried he would accidentally shoot a fireball, but he didn't
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:955
#, fuzzy
msgid "(There we go. Both power and control.)"
msgstr "（成了。既有威力，又具掌控。）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:959
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Mothersss protect me, can it be? Are you a sssecond great dragon of fire!? I "
"am blessssed to sssee sssuch thingsss in my time..."
msgstr ""
"母亲啊，护佑我吧，难道是真么回事？您难道就是那传说中的第二条圣焰巨龙吗？能在"
"有生之年得见此等奇景……实乃我三生之幸。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:963
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A drago— your great one is a dragon!? ...yes, I am a great dragon as well. "
"Do you not see my fire? Do you not see my flight?"
msgstr ""
"一条龙——你的那位“巨无霸”竟是一条龙！？……是的，我亦是一条巨龙。你难道不见我焚"
"天之火，不见我凌云之翼？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:973
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now you shall tell me where I may find the dragon —the other dragon. The two "
"of us have much business together."
msgstr ""
"如今，你需告知我，何处能寻得那条巨龙——即另一条巨龙。你我二人，尚有诸多要务需"
"共同料理。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:977
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, Great One, I hear you and obey! Follow me, and I will guide you to your "
"sister."
msgstr ""
"“伟大的存在啊，我听见您的召唤，必当遵从！请随我来，我将带您去见您的妹妹。”"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:1004
#, fuzzy
msgid "Everyone, keep moving! We’re running out of time."
msgstr "诸位，继续前进！时间不多了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:1052
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What’s this? Filthy humans grubbing around in our swamp? These lizards are "
"Blackcrest property!"
msgstr "这是何物？肮脏的人类竟在我们的沼泽里乱掘？这片地盘可是黑脊部族的领地！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:1056
#, fuzzy
msgid "They ssstrike at the matriarchsss! We ssshall ssslay them all!"
msgstr "他们向女族长发起突袭！我们定要杀尽他们！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:1060
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The main orcish army has caught up to us! Even if we defeat this vanguard "
"and flee onwards, we’ve missed our chance to break the saurian alliance..."
msgstr ""
"兽人主力大军已追上我们！即便击溃这路先锋并继续突围，我们已错失了瓦解蜥蜴人联"
"盟的良机……"

#. [scenario]: id=08x_Field_Hospital
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:6
msgid "Field Hospital"
msgstr "战地医院"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:112
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ah, much better. Thanks again for the healing, old man, but I’m afraid this "
"is the last we’ll be seeing of each other for some time."
msgstr ""
"啊，好多了。再次多谢您的治愈，老伙计，但恐怕此后很长一段时间，我们都要暂别"
"了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:116
#, fuzzy
msgid "Oh? You’ve been pulled back from the front?"
msgstr "哦？你竟被从前线撤回了？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:120
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Not quite. Remember Delfador’s prophecy? “Line of Kings”? “Sceptre of the "
"Wesfolk”?"
msgstr "并非如此。请记得德法多大师的预言吗？“王者血脉”？“韦诺民之权杖”？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:124
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Well, Garard’s worried. Queen’s gossip is that one of the nobles knows where "
"the long-lost Sceptre of Fire is. I dunno if that’s true, but e’ryone knows "
"that the king should hold the Sceptre. If a noble did get their hands on it "
"they’d have a pretty strong claim to Garard’s throne."
msgstr ""
"嗯，伽拉德很是担忧。王后那边的流言说，有位贵族知道那件失传已久的圣火权杖藏于"
"何处。我真不知此事真假，但人人都明白，权杖当由国王手持。若真让哪位贵族得逞，"
"那他们便有了足以觊觎伽拉德王位的强有力理由。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:128
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The king’s sendin’ me and an entire company of Weldyn’s most finest on a "
"’grand journey’ into the wildlands to find the Sceptre first, and ensure he "
"stays firmly in power."
msgstr ""
"国王正派我和威尔德恩最精锐的一整支部队踏上所谓的“伟大征程”，深入荒野，只为先"
"寻回圣火权杖，并确保他牢牢把持王权。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:132
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Good gods, why now? Wesnoth is in enough trouble as it is, without worrying "
"about lost artifacts and suicide missions."
msgstr ""
"神明在上，为何偏偏是此刻？韦诺王国本就祸患缠身，实在无力再为那些失落的圣物与"
"自杀式的任务操心半分。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:136
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You know how the king can be when he gets his mind set on somethin’. And if "
"someone really is trying to usurp the throne... Well, I only hope I can find "
"the Sceptre quickly, and resume my place at the king’s side."
msgstr ""
"你知道国王一旦下定决心会变成什么样子。倘若真有人企图篡夺王位……唉，我只希望我"
"能尽快寻得圣火权杖，重返陛下身侧。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. this mirrors Deoran's request to Delfador in S10x
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:147
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Lionel! You don’t... <b><i>have</i></b> to go, you know. You’re Garard’s top "
"general — if you refuse, I’m not sure there’s much he could do about it."
msgstr ""
"莱昂内尔！你不必……非得去不可，你心里清楚。你是伽拉德麾下的首席将军——若你执意"
"拒绝，我倒不确定他还能有何作为。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:151
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And it would be for the king’s own good! Garard needs you <b><i>here</i></"
"b>, Lionel! Wesnoth needs you here."
msgstr ""
"这全是为了国王陛下的大计！伽拉德需要你的<u><b>在这里</b></u>，莱昂内尔！韦诺"
"需要你在<font color=\"red\"><b>这里</b></font>！"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#. [message]: speaker=Omaranth
#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:155
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:136
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:311
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:744
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:282
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:338
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:406
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:287
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:857
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1471
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:198
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08x_Field_Hospital.cfg:159
msgid "I’m loyal, Methor. Always have been, always will be."
msgstr "我是忠诚的，梅瑟。始终如此，亦将永远如此。"

#. [scenario]: id=09_Omaranth
#. [unit]: id=Omaranth
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:13
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:804
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:332
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:419
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:197
msgid "Omaranth"
msgstr "奥玛兰斯"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:45
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:36
msgid "Omaranth’s Flight"
msgstr "奥玛兰斯之翼"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:63
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:60
#, fuzzy
msgid "Fauna"
msgstr "fauna（生态系统）兽类"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:94
msgid "30 gold"
msgstr "30金币"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:101
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Whoever destroyed this place did not care to loot it. We’ve gained 30 more "
"gold for our treasury."
msgstr "摧毁此地之人，并未动意劫掠分毫。我等国库，因此得增三十金币。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. $saurian_guide_name is a female saurian name generated with the default Wesnoth name generator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:155
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What ails you, $saurian_guide_name? I have trusted you thus far as a sign of "
"good faith — please don’t make me regret that decision."
msgstr ""
"你究竟有何苦衷，$saurian_guide_name？我至今视你为盟友，以此作为善意的证明——切"
"莫让我后悔这个决定。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:159
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh Great One, the other Great One livesss in thessse cold mountain "
"sssnowsss. But it is dangerousss! I am eldessst of my tribe... near "
"sssixteen years of age. Age hasss made me weak; too weak to travel thessse "
"landsss without help."
msgstr ""
"伟大的存在啊，另一位伟大的存在正栖息于那些冰冷的雪山之中。但这行路极其凶险！"
"我乃是我部族中最年长者……年岁已近十六（蜥蜴人之岁）。岁月使我衰弱，若无相助，"
"我实难踏足这片土地。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:163
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But you are young! You are mighty! Your fire ssshall warm usss in the cold "
"and protect usss from the dangersss! Together, yesss, together we ssshall "
"reach the valley!"
msgstr ""
"但你们尚年少！亦身怀伟力！你们的烈焰必将温暖严寒，护我们免受灾厄！携手，是"
"的，携手，我们将抵达山谷！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#. $saurian_guide_name will be a female saurian name generated with the default Wesnoth name generator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:179
#, fuzzy
msgid "Move $saurian_guide_name to the marked hex"
msgstr "将 $saurian_guide_name 移动至标记的格子上"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#. $saurian_guide_name will be a female saurian name generated with the default Wesnoth name generator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:188
msgid "Death of $saurian_guide_name"
msgstr "$saurian_guide_name 死亡"

#. [note]
#. $saurian_guide_name will be a female saurian name generated with the default Wesnoth name generator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:197
msgid "$saurian_guide_name will not follow you to the next scenario."
msgstr "$saurian_guide_name 不会跟你到下一个场景。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. $saurian_guide_name will be a female saurian name generated with the default Wesnoth name generator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:216
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"$saurian_guide_name, could we not have brought augurs along on this journey? "
"I’ve mastered many forms of magic, but the light of a healer is beyond my "
"reach."
msgstr ""
"<saurian_guide_name>，此次远行，我们为何不带上一位预言者同行？我虽已掌控诸多"
"奥术，却唯独难以触及治愈之光的真谛。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#. the matriarch assumes both Delfador and the drake are female
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:221
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh Great One, you know it isss forbidden! The malesss are not permitted! "
"Only you and I; usss femalesss may look upon the other Great One; your "
"sssister, our massster, our god!"
msgstr ""
"伟大者啊，您知晓这是禁忌！男性不被允许！唯有您与我；唯有我们女性，方能窥视那"
"另一位伟大者——您的姐妹，我们的主宰，我们的神明！"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:225
msgid "Us females? Err, yes, that’s right."
msgstr "我们女性？呃，是的，没错。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:244
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"So many bones! And they don’t look human... Is such death all work of your "
"great dragon?"
msgstr ""
"这么多白骨！而且它们看起来绝非人类……这般死状，难道全是你那条巨龙大军的杰作？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#. there were living drakes here only 20-30 years ago, but saurians have a very short lifespan.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:249
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"No, this valley is cursssed... My grandmother usssed to sssay there were "
"once many powerful creaturesss in thisss place, but they were ssslain long "
"before I wasss hatched. Now only our Great One remainsss."
msgstr ""
"不，这片山谷被诅咒了……我的祖母曾说过，此地昔日曾盘踞着许多强大的生灵，但在我"
"破壳而出之前，它们便已尽数毙命。如今，唯余我们的“大龙”尚存。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:253
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But once you find her, then there ssshall be two! Together the Great Onesss "
"will be unssstoppable!"
msgstr "但一旦你找到了她，那么便将是双数！至高者们合体之后，必将无懈可击！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:265
#, fuzzy
msgid "Oh Great One! Sssave me!"
msgstr "伟大的存在啊！救救我！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:281
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The sssnow, the windsss, it chillsss usss... Oh Great One, even with your "
"warmth, we cannot ssstay here long!"
msgstr ""
"这皑皑白雪，凛冽寒风，刺骨入骨……哦，伟大者啊，即便有您的暖流，我们也无法在此"
"久留！"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:285
msgid "We must keep moving."
msgstr "我们必须继续前行。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:293
#, fuzzy
msgid "The cold chillsss me ssso! I cannot sssurvive much longer!"
msgstr "这刺骨的寒意……折磨得我如此痛苦！我恐怕……活不久了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:301
msgid "Ssso... cccold... Oh Great One, I have failed you..."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:348
#, fuzzy
msgid "Well?"
msgstr "怎么，德法多大师？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:352
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yesss, oh Great One, thisss is the place! Thisss is the lair of the other "
"Great One, your sssister, our massster, our god!"
msgstr ""
"是——啊，伟大的存在，此地——正是！此地乃另一位伟大者的巢穴，您的姐妹，我们的主"
"宰，我们的神祇！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$saurian_guide_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:360
msgid ""
"Sssimply continue down the valley, and you ssshall meet your sssissster! I "
"dare go no further. Oh massstersss, please forgive usss..."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:479
msgid ""
"Hmph. What’s she so afraid of. Dragons are powerful, but hardly invulnerable."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:485
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The poets will sing my praises through the streets of Weldyn! After all, the "
"heroes of old used to slay dragons all the time."
msgstr ""
"诗人定将在韦林城的街道上歌颂我的功绩！毕竟，昔日的英雄们可曾将屠龙视为寻常？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:491
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Well, now that I think of it, I only remember reading about one single slain "
"dragon, many years ago."
msgstr "嗯，如今想来，我记忆中关于 slain dragon 的记载，唯有多年前的那一头。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:497
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And Prince Haldric did have a whole company of the Green Isle’s best knights "
"to help..."
msgstr "“哈尔德里克亲王确实得到了一支由绿岛最顶尖骑士组成的整编部队助阵……”"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:503
msgid "Ah."
msgstr "啊。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Omaranth
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:521
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"SOMETHING STIRS.\n"
"A HUMAN COMES."
msgstr ""
"异象涌动。\n"
"凡人将至。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Omaranth
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:528
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"IT IS FEEBLE.\n"
"IT IS WEAK.\n"
"IT WILL DIE."
msgstr ""
"此乃微弱。\n"
"此乃虚弱。\n"
"必将陨落。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:535
msgid ""
"...wait a minute, that’s not a dragon, it’s merely a drake! The saurians "
"must have mistaken it for a true dragon on account of its fire breath."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:539
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"So you are the villain behind all of this. You threaten my home and you "
"threaten my king — my friend."
msgstr "原来你便是这一切的幕后黑手。你威胁我的家园，威胁我的君王——我挚友。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:550
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hey, get back here!"
msgstr "喂，给我回来！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:557
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This drake is important — we cannot let it escape. My companions, I task you "
"to guard this cave entrance while I chase the drake inside. I know not why "
"it and the saurians that worship it are warring against Wesnoth, but I do "
"know they must be stopped."
msgstr ""
"这条幼龙至关重要——绝不能让它逃脱。我的同伴们，我命你们守卫此洞穴入口，待我深"
"入追击幼龙。我虽不知它及其所供奉蜥蜴人为何要与韦诺王国兵戎相见，但我知道，此"
"事必须予以制止。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:588
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You got it, boss. We’ll watch the cave entrance, and make sure you don’t get "
"trapped inside."
msgstr "包在我们身上，老大。我们会守好洞穴入口，确保您不会被困在里面。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:599
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Sounds like a pretty easy job. All we gots to do is wait ’round here for the "
"boss to come back out."
msgstr "听起来挺容易的。咱们只要在这蹲着，等那当头的再出来就行。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:607
#, fuzzy
msgid "Relax. What could go wrong?"
msgstr "放松。还能出什么岔子呢？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:614
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1087
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1122
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this scenario $companion_name is your leader, and can recruit / recall."
msgstr "在此战役中，$companion_name 是你的领袖，可招募或召回单位。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:746
#, fuzzy
msgid "Look out! One of them was lurking just inside the cave entrance!"
msgstr "小心！其中一个就潜伏在洞穴入口内侧！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:757
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That’s the last one ’o them, and with all the caves collapsed there won’t be "
"more! Nothing left to do but wait for Delfador to come back out, and "
"relax... for real this time. Great work everybody."
msgstr ""
"那是最后一只了。如今洞穴尽数坍塌，绝不会有更多了！剩下的事，便是等德法多平安"
"归来，好好放松一番……这次可是真的放松了。各位干得漂亮！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: role=escort1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:934
#, fuzzy
msgid "Brrr... It’s suddenly so c-c-cold..."
msgstr "呼……怎么突然变得这么……冷……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: id=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:966
#, fuzzy
msgid "Uhh, hello? Who’s there? Boss, is that you?"
msgstr "呃……你好？是谁在那儿？老板，是你吗？"

#. [message]: role=escort1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1020
msgid "Aaaah!"
msgstr "啊啊！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: role=escort1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1033
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hell no! Curse it all, I didn’t sign up for fighting zombies!"
msgstr "想都别想！该死，我可不是来跟亡灵死斗的！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1037
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"C’mon everyone, grab your weapons and get ready. I’ve a feeling we’re about "
"to have the fight of our lives!"
msgstr "都来！所有人，拿起武器，准备就绪！我有一种预感，我们即将迎来生死之战！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1076
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1108
#, fuzzy
msgid "Protect Delfador’s cave entrance until turns run out"
msgstr "在回合耗尽前，守护德法多的洞穴入口，直至获胜条件达成。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1080
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1112
#, fuzzy
msgid "Delfador’s cave entrance is destroyed"
msgstr "德法多的洞穴入口已遭毁灭"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1103
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Look, a frozen cave, just like the one Delfador went down! I’ll bet these’re "
"where all the undead are climbing out of. Quick now, if we knock down the "
"entrance we can trap the zombies inside!"
msgstr ""
"看，一座冰封的洞穴，和德法多下去的那座一模一样！我敢打赌，这里就是亡灵倾巢而"
"出的地方。快，只要我们堵住入口，就能把这些僵尸困在里面！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1119
#, fuzzy
msgid "Destroy hostile cave entrances to prevent enemies from emerging."
msgstr "摧毁敌方的洞穴入口，以阻止敌人现身。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1142
#, fuzzy
msgid "RraaaAAARRRGGG!"
msgstr "嗷——嗷——嗷！！！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1170
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ghost!! How’re we supposed to fight something our weapons can barely touch!?"
msgstr "鬼怪！！我们的武器连碰都碰不到，该怎么跟这种东西打？！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1204
#, fuzzy
msgid "Wha— what’s happening!?"
msgstr "什……怎么回事！？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1221
#, fuzzy
msgid "The undead have gone! Thank the gods! It’s finally over."
msgstr "亡灵已经退散了！多谢诸神！这场劫难终于结束了。"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1225
msgid "I’m alive... I can’t believe it..."
msgstr "我还活着……这简直不可思议……"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1226
msgid "female^I’m alive... I can’t believe it..."
msgstr "我还活着……这简直不可思议……"

#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1230
msgid "I think we won! ...but how?"
msgstr "我想我们赢了！……但怎么做到的？"

#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1231
msgid "female^I think we won! ...but how?"
msgstr "我想我们赢了！……但怎么做到的？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1261
#, fuzzy
msgid "The center crypt’s collapsing! We’ve failed!"
msgstr "中心墓穴正在崩塌！我们失败了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/09_Omaranth.cfg:1265
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We did our best, but the boss ain’t comin’ back out anytime soon. We’d "
"better scram back down south before the same happens to us."
msgstr ""
"我们已拼尽全力，但那掌权的家伙短期内怕是休想再露面。趁遭他毒手前，咱们最好赶"
"紧撤往南方。"

#. [scenario]: id=10_Houses_of_the_Dead
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:6
msgid "Houses of the Dead"
msgstr "亡灵之屋"

#. [message]
#. notice that appears at the beginning of the scenario if you select Brutal difficulty
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:104
msgid "Meanwhile..."
msgstr "与此同时……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:132
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Stand and fight me, drake! You and your saurians have caused Wesnoth enough "
"harm. In the name of King Garard, your villainy ends here."
msgstr ""
"起身迎战吧，龙蜥！你与你的蜥蜴人给韦诺带来的灾祸已够多了。为了伽拉德国王之"
"名，你的恶行至此终结！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:143
#, fuzzy
msgid "...I suppose we’ll have to do this the hard way."
msgstr "...我想，我们只得出此下策，以非常规手段破局了。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:151
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:346
msgid "Find Omaranth"
msgstr "寻获奥玛兰斯"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:213
#, fuzzy
msgid "A drakish tomb? This looks ominous..."
msgstr "龙族的陵墓？这景象……甚是不祥……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:257
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A ghost! Walking corpses are a great evil, but mastery over spirits is far "
"fouler still. Damned vessels, conscious but enslaved... yet where there are "
"enchantments, there are opportunities."
msgstr ""
"鬼魅！行尸走肉固乃大恶，然操弄亡魂更是可憎至极！这些被诅咒的躯壳，灵识尚存却"
"沦为囚徒……然而，魔咒既起，便蕴生机。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:267
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I must concentrate. The slightest mistake in the casting of this spell could "
"be fatal."
msgstr "我必须全神贯注。若这法术稍有差池，后果将不堪设想。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:283
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I call upon the name of An-Usrukhar the Great. I invoke the Mirror of "
"Evanescent Time!"
msgstr "我奉安-乌什鲁哈尔至尊之名！我召唤隐逝之镜！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:290
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I challenge life against death! I invoke freedom against order! I wield "
"light against darkness!"
msgstr "我以生命向死亡发起挑战！我呼唤自由以对抗秩序！我挥舞光明以驱散黑暗！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:297
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"May the coils of servitude be broken! Spirit of the damned, be freed from "
"your master."
msgstr "愿奴役的枷锁粉碎！受诅咒的亡魂，从你的主人手中解脱吧！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:315
#, fuzzy
msgid "My mind... is my own..."
msgstr "我的灵魂……依旧属于我自己……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:319
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Speak, spectre! Tell me of this place. Where is the drake they call the "
"“Great One”?"
msgstr ""
"“现身吧，幽灵！告知我此地之隐秘。他们所称颂的‘大帝’巨龙，究竟身在何处？”"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:323
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I do not know. I know nothing of drakes. I am a man. My name is Aethyr... I "
"had almost forgotten. I died long ago, in a great battle..."
msgstr ""
"我不知晓。我对这些飞龙一无所知。我乃凡人，名为埃瑟尔……我险些已将此名遗忘。我"
"早已在多年前的一场大战中殒命……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:325
#, fuzzy
msgid "Aethyr"
msgstr "以太"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:328
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re the spirit of a human? How did you come to roam these drakish halls, "
"so far from the lands of men?"
msgstr "你竟是人类的灵魄？竟是如何流落至此阴森殿堂，远离了人类的故土？"

#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Iliah-Malal brought me here. He made me promises of life renewed, but "
"instead bound me to his will. Perhaps Iliah-Malal will know of your drake."
msgstr ""
"伊利阿-玛拉尔带我来到此处。他曾许诺赋予我新生，却最终将我束缚于他的意志之下。"
"或许伊利阿-玛拉尔知晓你的龙人。"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:336
msgid ""
"A necromancer? Troubling. Yes, I should very much like to meet this Iliah-"
"Malal."
msgstr "一个死灵法师？麻烦。是的，我很乐意见一见伊利阿-玛拉尔。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:350
msgid "Find Iliah-Malal"
msgstr "找到伊利阿-玛拉尔"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:357
msgid ""
"Delfador can capture hostile ghosts by moving adjacent to them, unless he is "
"polymorphed."
msgstr ""

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:360
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:781
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1123
msgid "Allied ghosts will not follow you to the next scenario."
msgstr "结盟的鬼魂不会随你进入下一个场景。"

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:395
msgid "Ghost Captured"
msgstr "鬼魂已捕获"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:415
msgid "Sythan"
msgstr "西丹"

#. [message]: speaker=Sythan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:430
msgid ""
"I was once a great lord... I commanded armies! Iliah-Malal promised I would "
"lead again."
msgstr ""
"我曾是个伟大的领主……我统领军队！伊利阿-玛拉尔保证过我可以再次统帅军队了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Sythan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:434
#, fuzzy
msgid "It was all a lie. I became only his slave."
msgstr "这不过是一场谎言。我最终沦为他的奴仆。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:443
#, fuzzy
msgid "Vellin Ka"
msgstr "维林·卡"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=VellinKa
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:461
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your banners were red.\n"
"Your spears were sharp.\n"
"Your hearts were cold."
msgstr ""
"你们的旗帜染着血色，\n"
"你们的长矛锋利如霜，\n"
"然而你们的心，早已冰凉。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=VellinKa
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:467
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Iliah-Malal led your army.\n"
"Iliah-Malal burned our Eyrie.\n"
"Iliah-Malal will die."
msgstr ""
"伊利阿 - 玛拉尔率领你的大军。\n"
"伊利阿 - 玛拉尔焚毁了我们的高巢。\n"
"伊利阿 - 玛拉尔终将伏诛。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:473
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re a drake, and Iliah-Malal razed your home alongside... an army of "
"living men? And what of the drake called Omaranth; how did he survive if the "
"rest of you did not?"
msgstr ""
"你是一条龙，而伊利阿 - 玛拉尔与你那……一支由活人组成的军队联手，夷平了你赖以生"
"存的家园？那么，那条名叫奥玛兰斯的龙又是如何幸存下来的？毕竟你们其余的龙族难"
"道都未能幸免吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=VellinKa
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:477
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Omaranth was Dominant of our Flight.\n"
"Omaranth was strongest in our Eyrie.\n"
"Omaranth’s fate was not seen by I."
msgstr ""
"奥玛兰斯曾是我们群鹰中的主宰。\n"
"奥玛兰斯曾是我们鹰巢中最强者。\n"
"他的命运，我未曾窥见。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: id=$sun_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:510
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A passage to the world above! Oh, how I long to go through and see the sun "
"again..."
msgstr "一条通往上方世界的大门！哦，我多么渴望穿过它，再次沐浴阳光……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:514
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Focus, spirit. This necromancer Iliah-Malal must have raised these corpses, "
"and now sends them against my allies on the surface. We must not abandon our "
"task here."
msgstr ""
"凝神，灵体。死灵法师伊利阿 - 玛拉尔必是唤起了这些尸骸，此刻正驱使它们攻击我在"
"地表之上的盟友。我们绝不能在此刻放弃任务。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:527
msgid "Hagha-Tan"
msgstr "哈格哈-坦"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=HaghaTan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:542
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The chief called me to war... I knew the attack was risky, but I was "
"willing..."
msgstr "大酋长唤我征战……我知此袭凶险万分，然亦甘愿赴之……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:546
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you’re a recently-dead orc, does that mean you fell in battle against "
"Wesnoth? What can you tell me about your allies’ battle plans? Troop "
"movements?"
msgstr ""
"若你是一名刚刚逝去的兽人，这是否意味着你在与韦诺王国的征战中阵亡？你能告诉我"
"盟友们的作战计划吗？部队的部署动向如何？"

#. [message]: speaker=HaghaTan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:551
msgid "You are no lord of mine, man of Wesnoth. I serve only my clan."
msgstr "你不是我的领主，韦诺人。我只效忠于我的氏族。"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:561
msgid "Melinna"
msgstr "梅林娜"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:575
msgid ""
"Are you a drake? Do you know anything about Omaranth, or this necromancer "
"Iliah-Malal?"
msgstr "你是龙人？你是否知道奥玛兰斯，或者这位死灵法师伊利阿-玛拉尔？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Melinna
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:579
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I know only what I knew in life, Delfador. Yes, I recognize you... Garard’s "
"attack dog..."
msgstr "我所知的一切，不过是我生前所知，德法多。是的，我认得你……伽拉德的走狗……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Melinna
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:583
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I was once a lady of the court. But the dead found me in the night. Now I "
"find myself here, in a form reflecting my fate. Who helped undead sneak into "
"Wesnoth? Why didn’t you keep us all safe..."
msgstr ""
"我曾是一位王室贵胄。然而亡灵在暗夜中寻获了我。如今，我身处此境，这形态恰如我"
"命运的写照。究竟是谁助亡灵潜入韦诺？你们为何未保我等周全……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:617
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There is a gate here, sealed by runic energy. My magic should be able to "
"open it, but we must be prepared for whatever lies beyond."
msgstr ""
"此处有一扇大门，被符文能量封禁。以我的魔力或许能将其打开，但我们必须为门后的"
"未知做好准备。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:631
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Only Delfador has the power to open these gates... whatever lies beyond will "
"be most dangerous..."
msgstr ""
"只有德法多大师拥有开启这些大门的力量……无论门后潜藏着什么，都将是极度危险的……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:651
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Whatever lurks behind this gate, it will be dangerous. I should make sure I "
"am prepared before I proceed."
msgstr "无论门后潜藏着什么，定是凶险万分。在下须先做好准备，方能前行。"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:653
msgid "Open the gate"
msgstr "打开大门"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:658
msgid "Wait"
msgstr "等等"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:748
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You! With so many undead about I was expecting to find the necromancer... I "
"don’t entirely understand what’s going on here, but I do know that you’re an "
"enemy of Wesnoth, and that’s good enough for me."
msgstr ""
"你！此处亡灵肆虐，我本以为能寻到那名死灵法师……我虽未完全参透眼前究竟何故，但"
"我知道你乃韦诺的仇敌，这便足够了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Omaranth
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:752
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"YOU INVADE MY HOME.\n"
"YOU SLAY MY SERVANTS.\n"
"YOU UNDERSTAND NOTHING."
msgstr ""
"汝侵吾家。\n"
"汝杀吾仆。\n"
"汝，一无所知。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Omaranth
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:758
#, fuzzy
msgid "NOW, YOU DIE."
msgstr "此刻，你命归尘土。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:774
msgid "Defeat Omaranth"
msgstr "击败奥玛兰斯"

#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:844
msgid "Ah ha, ha ha ha..."
msgstr "啊哈，哈哈哈……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:849
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Well fought, Delfador! They warned me you were dangerous, but to have found "
"me amidst all the vastness of the north — you have truly exceeded all "
"expectations!"
msgstr ""
"干得漂亮，德法多！他们曾警告过我，你危险至极，但你竟能在北方那片广袤无垠之地"
"寻得我——你当真彻底超出了我的所有预料！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:853
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now the story begins to make sense. The Omaranth I saw was never more than "
"an illusion. You are Iliah-Malal."
msgstr ""
"如今，这段故事终于显露出真容。我所见之奥玛兰斯，不过是一场幻象。你才是伊利阿 "
"- 玛拉尔。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:857
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You wiped out this flight of drakes, and took the visage of their leader. "
"You led the saurians to join Clan Blackcrest, and you sent them to war "
"against Wesnoth. But why? How does all this fighting benefit a mage?"
msgstr ""
"你屠灭了那支龙蜥部队，并夺取了其首领的面容。你煽动蜥蜴人加入黑冠氏族，更驱使"
"他们向韦诺王国发动战争。但究竟为何？这一切厮杀，对一名法师又能有何裨益？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:861
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"How does all <i><b>your</b></i> fighting benefit <i><b>you</b></i>? Decades "
"of war, and what has been gained? While you bleed for a failing country and "
"an aging king, your whole life is passing you by. You’re on the wrong side "
"of history, Delfador war-mage."
msgstr ""
"你所有的<em><b>战斗</b></em>究竟能为你带来什么？数十年的战火纷飞，究竟换来了"
"什么？当你为一个行将就木的国度、一位垂垂老矣的国王而流血牺牲时，你的一生也在"
"悄然流逝。德法多，战争法师，你站在历史错误的一方。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:866
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But you don’t have to be. Walk away! Stop wasting your life in service of an "
"old man, and finally act for yourself! Delfador, I have allies under whose "
"patronage you could live like a king, if you would only accept them!"
msgstr ""
"但你本不必如此。转身离去吧！别再为你的生命浪费在为一个老者的效劳中，终于为自"
"己而活吧！德法多，在我那些盟友的庇护下，只要你愿意接纳他们，你便能活得如君王"
"一般！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:870
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Like a king? I already serve a king, Iliah-Malal, and am well-loved for it. "
"Protecting Wesnoth is my <b><i>duty</i></b>. King Garard is my <b><i>friend</"
"i></b>. I hope you did not think to break me down so easily."
msgstr ""
"“像国王那样？我早已效忠一位君王——伊利阿-玛拉尔，且因其忠诚而深得其爱戴。守护"
"韦诺，乃我之<b><i>职责</i></b>；伽拉德王，乃我之<b><i>挚友</i></b>。你莫要以"
"为能如此轻易地将我击垮。”"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:874
#, fuzzy
msgid "Bah, remain a fool, then. You will not find me so easily broken either."
msgstr "哼，继续当你的蠢货吧。想要轻易击溃我，你也办不到。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:915
#, fuzzy
msgid "Powers of darkness, confound my foes!"
msgstr "黑暗之力，扰乱我的仇敌！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1116
#, fuzzy
msgid "Find and defeat Iliah-Malal, before his undead overwhelm you."
msgstr "在亡灵大军将你淹没之前，寻找到并击败伊利阿-玛拉尔。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1138
#, fuzzy
msgid "Nice try, Delfador! You’ve only destroyed another illusion."
msgstr "好计谋，德法多！你不过是又毁掉了一重幻象罢了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1160
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"So you have found the real me. No matter. I shall have you yet, Delfador!"
msgstr "既然你已寻得真正的我，那也无妨。德法多，我终将把你收入囊中！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1175
#, fuzzy
msgid "Shadows consume you!"
msgstr "阴影将吞噬你！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Iliah-Malal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1188
#, fuzzy
msgid "I should... have kept... my potion..."
msgstr "我本该……保管好……我的魔药……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1211
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Elende’s prophecy rings true once more: <i>“A figure of shadow cloaked in "
"the spirits of the dead”</i>... Good riddance. His meddling in life and "
"death has been the cause of great evil."
msgstr ""
"艾莲德的预言再次应验：<i>“一个身披亡魂的阴影之影”</i>……如释重负。他妄图干涉生"
"死，正是造成巨大灾祸的根源。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1228
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I am free... free! You have breathed into me a ravenousness for life anew, "
"life to drain from those who roam unfettered under the pale sun. Take us "
"into your service, Delfador; lead us to your foes! Lead us against the "
"living!"
msgstr ""
"我重获自由……自由了！你在我心中注入了对生命的全新渴望，那是一种从那些在无拘无"
"束的苍白阳光下游荡者身上汲取的饥渴。请接纳吾等为您所用，德法多大师；引领我们"
"走向您的仇敌！带领我们向活物宣战！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1232
msgid ""
"No, no! Do not tempt me, I beg you, for that way madness lies... should I "
"ever start down that dark path I would never become free of it."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1236
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"No. But you have been of great service today, and for that you shall be "
"rewarded with peace."
msgstr "不。但今日你立下大功，吾将以安宁作为对你的酬谢。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1250
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Return to your land of calm and quiet, and trouble the living no longer. I "
"shall save my country without your help."
msgstr ""
"回到你那宁静祥和的故土去吧，莫再惊扰生者。无需你的援手，我也将保全我的国度。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=10_Houses_of_the_Dead
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1275
#, fuzzy
msgid "From the dead I came, and to the dead I return..."
msgstr "我源自死亡，终归死亡……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=10_Houses_of_the_Dead
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1276
#, fuzzy
msgid "Rock and dust, bone and stone..."
msgstr "磐石与尘灰，骸骨与金石……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=10_Houses_of_the_Dead
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1277
#, fuzzy
msgid "Avenge my flight..."
msgstr "为我逃离此恨复仇……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=10_Houses_of_the_Dead
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1278
#, fuzzy
msgid "Good luck, Delfador... Don’t trust anyone..."
msgstr "祝你好运，德法多……切勿轻信任何人……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just killed an enemy ghost. That's not a good thing - if he moves next to hostile ghosts without killing them, he can take control of them.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10_Houses_of_the_Dead.cfg:1289
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That one has returned to the land of the dead. Maybe I could have captured "
"it, if only I’d had a chance to try."
msgstr "那个魂魄已重返死域。若我当初能有试手的机会，或许本可将其收服。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=10x_Elensefar_Outskirts
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:6
#, fuzzy
msgid "Elensefar Outskirts"
msgstr "埃仁撒伐郊外"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Maddock
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:99
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The answer is no. Garard, Elensefar has no interest in joining your little "
"war-clique. You’ve already stirred up enough trouble; trade up the river is "
"failing, and goblins are once again raiding my northern border."
msgstr ""
"答案是“不”。伽拉德，埃仁撒伐无意加入你那微不足道的战争小圈子。你们制造的麻烦"
"已经够多了；河上的贸易正日趋凋敝，而哥布林又一次袭扰着我的北方边境。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:103
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All the more reason to join forces and wipe the orcs out! Think how much "
"territory we could command if the Northlands were fully open to human "
"settlement."
msgstr ""
"正因此，我们更应联手将兽人彻底肃清！试想，若北方诸地完全向人类开放，我们将能"
"统御多少疆土。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Maddock
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:107
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you were <i>winning</i>, certainly, but then we wouldn’t be speaking "
"together here, would we? You’ve never been one for sharing the spoils."
msgstr ""
"若你真能<em>获胜</em>，那倒不错；可若真如此，此刻我们便不会在此对坐长谈，不是"
"吗？你从来就不是个懂得与人分享战利品的人。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Maddock
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:111
#, fuzzy
msgid "Now if you’ll excuse me, warmonger, I have a city to govern."
msgstr "若肯赐教，好战之徒，我得去治理我的城池了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:124
#, fuzzy
msgid "Damn his cowardice! Still no word from Lionel?"
msgstr "哼，这懦夫！莱昂内尔将军那边还是没有消息吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:128
#, fuzzy
msgid "(stares)"
msgstr "（凝视）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:132
#, fuzzy
msgid "Speak UP, boy! I raised you to be a killer, not a coward!"
msgstr "大声点，小子！我把你养大是让你成为杀手，不是懦夫！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:136
#, fuzzy
msgid "You hardly raised me at all..."
msgstr "你几乎从未养育过我……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:140
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, confound it. Why did I let those infernal rumors convince me to send "
"away my best general and most loyal soldiers?\n"
"\n"
"Lionel is missing in action, Arand becomes more paranoid by the day, and you "
"still speak softer than a mouse. This is war — Wesnoth needs a warrior "
"prince."
msgstr ""
"唉，真是该死！为何我当时竟让那些该死的流言惑，遣走了我麾下最优秀的将军和最忠"
"诚的士兵？\n"
"\n"
"如今莱昂内尔下落不明，阿兰德亲王一日比一日多疑，而你依旧言语轻柔，弱如微鼠。"
"这乃是一场战争——韦诺王国急需一位尚武的王子！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:146
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Even reliable Delfador took off months ago on some wild goose chase in the "
"Northlands. Some days it feels like the whole world is moving against me... "
"perhaps it is an omen of things to come."
msgstr ""
"就连一向可靠的德法多也在数月前启程，北境去追寻那虚无缥缈的幻想了。有时，这世"
"道真让人觉着万事皆在作对……这，或许就是未来降临的预兆。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:153
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The coward’s option once more rears its ugly head. Negotiate, capitulate; "
"yield the border to the butchers. Give unto the orcs their pound of flesh."
msgstr ""
"懦夫的选择再次狰狞现身：谈判，投降，将边境割让给那些屠夫。向兽人献上一磅血"
"肉。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:157
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"How many would die? How many have already died to this problem of my own "
"making? I can already feel the kings of old judging me in my failure, my "
"squandering of everything they fought so hard to build..."
msgstr ""
"究竟会有多少人死去？又有多少人已经因这由我亲手酿成的祸患而命丧黄泉？我仿佛已"
"能感受到先王们在因我的失败而审判我，因我挥霍了他们拼死奋斗才建立的一切……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:162
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"No. I will not go down in history as a failed king; a weakling, a coward "
"powerless to protect his people against the savages beyond. I have chosen "
"the path of war, and I will see it through to its bloody end."
msgstr ""
"不。我绝不会在历史上留下一个失败君主、懦弱者，或无力保护子民免受外邦蛮族侵扰"
"的无能统治者的耻辱。我已选择了战争之路，必将将其血染到底，誓死不休。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/10x_Elensefar_Outskirts.cfg:167
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Riders, summon the reserves. Empty Halstead! Empty Weldyn! I want every "
"child old enough to walk and every elder young enough to stand!\n"
"\n"
"In two weeks time we march across the ford and assault the Blackcrest war-"
"camp. Come hell or high water, we will yet have our victory."
msgstr ""
"骑兵们，召集后备部队！哈尔斯蒂德，清空！维尔德因，清空！我要每一个能走路的孩"
"童，每一个尚能站立的老人！\n"
"\n"
"两周后，我们将渡过雅碧滩，强攻黑脊兽营。无论地狱烈火还是滔天洪水，我们终将凯"
"旋。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=11_Clan_Blackcrest
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:13
#, fuzzy
msgid "Galcadar"
msgstr "加尔卡德"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:51
#, fuzzy
msgid "Saurian Defectors"
msgstr "蜥蜴人叛徒"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Orcish Sovereign, id=Ghuvog
#. [unit]: type=Orcish Sovereign, id=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:171
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1129
#, fuzzy
msgid "Chief Ghuvog"
msgstr "酋长古沃格"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Drakefador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:338
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Saurians of Saurgrath! It is I, your Great One, bringing an even greater "
"warning!"
msgstr "斯奥格的蜥蜴人！是我，你们伟大的至尊，带来更可怕的警告！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Drakefador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:342
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"These orcs have, umm, conspired to betray you! You must strike first and "
"kill them all — now hear me and obey!"
msgstr ""
"这些兽人——呃，已经密谋背叛你了！你必须先发制人，将他们尽数剿灭——现在听我号"
"令，即刻执行！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=defector4
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:347
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Can it be? The Great One ssspeaksss to usss! I am not worthy! I am blessed "
"to hear your great voice, unusssual though it may be!"
msgstr ""
"岂有此事？伟大者竟与我们说话！我实在不配！能聆听您的宏声，实乃大幸，纵使这声"
"音略显奇特，亦是如此！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=defector3
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:355
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yesss, the great fiery one has sssaved usss! If the orcsss will betray us, "
"then we mussst ssstrike firssst!"
msgstr ""
"是了，那位伟大的火之主宰拯救了我们！若那群兽人打算背叛，那我们也必须先发制"
"人！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=defector2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:359
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...caution, caution, ssomething isss not right! Where are the ssseven "
"matriarchsss? Why does the Great One ssspeak ssso nasssally?"
msgstr ""
"……当心，当心，有、有、有哪里不对劲！七位母皇在哪里？那位“至尊者”为何说话如"
"此、如此……阴险？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=defector3
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:364
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Do you not sssee her majesssty? It isss not our place to quessstion the "
"great fiery one!"
msgstr "难道你没看见陛下的尊容吗？我等岂敢妄议那伟大的火之本尊！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:368
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Shut it, all of you! I don’t know why any of youse care what some off-brand "
"dragon says, but don’t forget that you lizards made a deal to fight with us "
"against Wesnoth. Even paid <i>us</i> for the privilege, you dumb little "
"worms!\n"
"\n"
"Now form up and get in line, before I have to beat some discipline into you!"
msgstr ""
"都给我闭嘴！我不知道你们这群蜥蜴人为什么在乎那条赝品巨龙说些什么，但别忘了，"
"你们蜥蜴人与我们达成过协议，要并肩作战对抗韦诺！甚至还要**付钱**给我们这份“荣"
"耀”，你们这些愚蠢的小虫子！\n"
"\n"
"现在列队站好！否则我就动手给你们“好好”上一课！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=defector1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:378
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You insssult usss! Worssse, you dare insssult the Great One! Curssses upon "
"you, cursses upon you! We ssshall fight you, we mussst fight you!"
msgstr ""
"你竟敢**亵渎**我们！更过分的是，你竟敢**冒犯伟大者**！**诅咒**你，**诅咒**"
"你！我们必将与你**战斗**，我们**必须**与你**战斗**！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=defector3
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:386
#, fuzzy
msgid "Yesss, we mussst fight! Fight the orcsss!"
msgstr "是——是——我们必——须——战——斗！去杀——杀那些兽——兽人！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:390
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh yeah? Try me, you filthy sacks of lizard slime; I’ll teach youse your "
"proper place! To arms, Blackcrests!!"
msgstr ""
"哦？敢来试试吗？你们这些肮脏的蜥蜴 slime 囊，老子这就教教你们什么叫安分守己！"
"黑冠氏族的兽人们，拿起武器！！哦？哈？敢来试试吗？你们这些肮脏的蜥蜴脓包，老"
"子这就教教你们什么叫安分守己！黑冠氏族的兽人们，抄起家伙！！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:462
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Wesnoth’s foes are thrown into chaos! Iliah-Malal’s illusion magic has done "
"much harm. In my hands, perhaps it can do some good."
msgstr ""
"韦诺的敌寇已陷入混乱！伊利阿 - 玛拉尔的幻术已酿成诸多灾祸。如今，此法落入我"
"手，或可转祸为福。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:466
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This is the great western horde — these tents have been a staging ground for "
"every Blackcrest attack on Wesnoth since they first entered the war, so many "
"years ago."
msgstr ""
"这便是威震西方的浩大魔军——自数十年前他们初次踏入战火以来，这些营帐便成了每一"
"场黑崖攻势对韦诺王国的集结之地。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:470
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Every time I tried to lead soldiers across the river, it was these "
"fortifications that pushed me back. ’tis a funny feeling to finally see them "
"from the north side."
msgstr ""
"每逢我率军渡河，皆是这些工事将我击退。如今能从北侧望见它们，倒真是一种奇妙的"
"滋味。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:474
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But more importantly, this is where the Blackcrest war-chief commands his "
"clan."
msgstr ""
"但更重要的是，此地正是黑 crest 氏族酋长统御其族群之所。但更重要的是，此地正是"
"黑齿氏族酋长统御其部众之所。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:480
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With most of the saurians defecting, this is our chance to kill the "
"Blackcrest chief and break their grip on the Abez once and for all. It’s all "
"led up to this! We can end things here and now!"
msgstr ""
"蜥蜴人大部已倒戈，此刻正是我们诛杀黑 crest 首领、彻底终结雅碧滩之祸的良机！万"
"事俱备，只待今日！我们就此了结一切！蜥蜴人大部已倒戈，此刻正是我们诛杀黑锋首"
"领、彻底终结雅碧滩之祸的良机！万事俱备，只待今日！我们就此了结一切！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:484
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For the sake of all Wesnoth, for the sake of King Garard, we cannot fail."
msgstr "为了整个韦诺王国的命运，为了加拉德国王，我们绝不能失败。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:493
#, fuzzy
msgid "Defeat Ghuvog, the Blackcrest war-chief"
msgstr "击败黑牙氏族酋长古沃格"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:511
msgid "Death of Garard"
msgstr "伽拉德死亡"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. in this string, $companion_name is female (probably "Lynyan")
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:538
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"female^Are you certain you’re prepared for this fight, $companion_name? "
"You’re an outlaw, not a soldier, and your posse has already bled more than I "
"paid you for. I shan’t lie and say your help is unneeded, but neither should "
"I take it for granted."
msgstr ""
"女：$companion_name，你当真已准备好迎接这场战斗了吗？你本是亡命之徒，而非统兵"
"之将，你的那帮伙计流过的血，恐怕已远超我付给你的酬劳。我不会虚言相饰说你的帮"
"助可有可无，但也绝不可将你的援手视作理所当然。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. in this string, $companion_name is male
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:544
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Are you certain you’re prepared for this fight, $companion_name? You’re an "
