# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:619
#, fuzzy
msgid "Now that’s more like it! Fall into line and get ready to fight."
msgstr "这才像话！列好队形，准备开打！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:633
#, fuzzy
msgid "You betray the Great One... the stars shall bring your doom..."
msgstr "你竟背叛那位伟大的存在……星辰必将降下你的末日……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:646
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Graahh!! Get out of here, you stinking pink-skins! Now is not a good time!"
msgstr "吼啊啊！！滚出这里，你们这群臭烘烘的粉皮家伙！现在可不是好时机！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:659
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hey, lay off my Shamans! Do you have any idea how hard it is to find those!?"
msgstr "嘿，别动我的萨满！你知道找到那些家伙有多难吗！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:671
#, fuzzy
msgid "Out of my face, worms!"
msgstr "滚出我的视线，虫豸！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. yes yes, Delfador probably hasn't attacked any orcs by now (and he might not be using fire). But it's a cool line.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:736
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ah-ha! I’d recognize that smell of burning orc-flesh anywhere – Delfador has "
"returned!"
msgstr "啊哈！无论何处，我都能认出这燃烧兽人尸骸的独特气息——德法多回来了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:745
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This is the chance I’ve been waiting for; my golden, desperate opportunity "
"to crush the orcs now and forever! Once more unto the breach – captain, "
"break me an opening through the enemy lines!"
msgstr ""
"这正是我苦等已久的良机——千载难逢的绝好时机，此刻一举粉碎兽人，永绝后患！“再度"
"冲锋，破开敌阵”——长官，为我撕开一条通往敌军防线的缺口！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:819
#, fuzzy
msgid "You heard the king; form up, and prepare to storm the front!"
msgstr "诸位听到了国王的号令；列阵完毕，即刻准备强攻前线！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:914
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran has rejoined Delfador’s party, and you have gained 100 extra gold!"
msgstr "德欧兰已加入德法多的队伍，你获得了额外 100 金币！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:916
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For the remainder of this campaign, Deoran is a leader — he can recruit "
"fresh royal soldiers (Spearmen, Bowmen, etc.) while standing on his keep."
msgstr ""
"在本战役的剩余部分中，德欧兰将成为统帅——当伫立于其据点时，他可招募崭新的皇家"
"士兵（长矛兵、弓箭手等）。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:945
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For Wesnoth! For victory! By battle and blood, for fury and flame, and the "
"triumph of my people!"
msgstr "为了韦诺！为了胜利！以战火与鲜血，以狂怒与烈焰，成就我族的凯旋！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:963
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All right, all right, I know when I’m beat! Let’s not be hasty, there’s no "
"need for more death and violence. <span size='x-small'>Against me, anyhow. "
"Nasty pink-skin whelps.</span>"
msgstr ""
"好，好，我知道我输了！咱们别急着动手，没必要再平添死伤和暴行……当然，是没必要"
"对我这样。那些讨厌的粉皮小鬼。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:974
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Watch your tongue, vermin! I am no ’whelp’, but King Garard of Wesnoth, "
"second of his name!\n"
"\n"
"And in that name, for the Kingdom of Wesnoth, I hereby annex these lands "
"from the Great River in the south to the foothills of the Heart Mountains in "
"the north! You orcs shall fall beneath our swords as wheat before the scythe!"
msgstr ""
"小心你的舌头，卑鄙的杂种！我并非什么“小崽子”，而是韦诺王国的加罗德二世国"
"王！\n"
"就以此名，为了韦诺王国，我正式宣布：将这片土地从南方的泰河一直划归到北方心山"
"脉的脚下！你们这些兽人，必将在我们的剑下伏尸，宛如镰刀前的麦秆！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:980
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...but I am no fool. Wesnoth is tired of war, and your lord Garard is "
"nothing if not merciful. I will spare your life and the life of your "
"warriors, on one condition.\n"
"\n"
"You must hereby swear an oath to gather both your clan from here, and Clan "
"Whitefang from the hills around Fort Garard. You shall leave these lands and "
"never return so long as I draw breath, on pain of death!"
msgstr ""
"……但我绝非愚钝之辈。韦诺已厌倦了战争，而您的领主伽拉德，其仁慈更是人所共知。"
"我将赦免你及其麾下战士的性命，但只有一个条件。\n"
"\n"
"你须在此立下誓言，率领你部族离开此地，并召集高特伽拉德要塞四周山峦中的白牙氏"
"族。只要我德法多尚存一息，你们便必须离开这片土地，永世不得返回；违者，必死无"
"疑！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:986
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yeah yeah yeah, whatever you say. We was just leaving; isn’t that right, "
"boys? <span size='x-small'>Nasty filthy pink-skins.</span>"
msgstr ""
"“行了行了，随便你说吧。我们这就走了，对吧，兄弟们？<span size='x-small'>脏兮"
"兮的粉红皮。</span>\""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:1003
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"After all this time... Wesnoth is finally at peace. It is as if a veil of "
"shadows has been lifted from upon my eyes!"
msgstr ""
"历经数载沧桑……韦诺终于重归宁静。仿佛有一层阴影的帷幕，自我的眼前悄然揭去！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:1007
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, you rascal, you’ve truly outdone yourself this time. They tell me "
"how you turned the saurians against the orcs, sowed chaos from behind; truly "
"incredible!"
msgstr ""
"德法多，你这无赖，这次真是青出于蓝！传闻你煽动蜥蜴人对抗兽人，在幕后播下混乱"
"的种子——这简直是不可思议！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:1011
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador the “Great One”, hah! Now that’s the stuff legends are made of. So "
"legendary, in fact..."
msgstr "德法多大师这位“伟大者”，哈！这才真正配得上传说的素材。简直传奇到……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:1021
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"“The Great” you were called by the enemy, and “The Great” you shall be "
"called until the end of your days. Kneel, Delfador, war-mage of Wesnoth. And "
"rise, “Delfador the Great”, High Advisor to the Crown!"
msgstr ""
"“大贤者”曾是敌人对你的称呼，这份名号也将伴随你直至生命尽头。跪下吧，德法多，"
"韦诺的战争法师。继而起身，成为“德法多大师”——王室的最高顾问！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:1039
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now come, let us celebrate my— our— ...all right, <i><b>your</b></i> "
"success! Victory! Victory! Victory by the name of Delfador!!"
msgstr ""
"来，让我们庆祝我的——我们的——算了，<i><b>你的</b></i>胜利！胜利！胜利！由德法"
"多大师名垂千古的胜利！！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11_Clan_Blackcrest.cfg:1066
#, fuzzy
msgid "Huh."
msgstr "哼。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
