#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh ho, someone fetch me more wine! The night’s still young; I’m ready for a "
"proper CELEBRATION!!"
msgstr "哦嚯，来人，再给我端些酒来！夜色尚浅，我正期待一场真正的**庆典**！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:161
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I started as an inglorious apprentice, without even a name to call my own. "
"And now I have saved Wesnoth from war, and in the process become the king’s "
"most trusted advisor! Truly, this is more than I could have ever hoped for."
msgstr ""
"我初出茅庐时，不过是个默默无闻的学徒，甚至连像样的名字都不曾拥有。而今，我已"
"将韦诺王国从战火中解救，更在此过程中，成为国王最信赖的顾问！诚然，这已远超我"
"昔日一切期许。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:165
#, fuzzy
msgid "I’m giddy with joy... or perhaps ’tis also the wine, heh."
msgstr "我心中狂喜……或者，这酒也添了几分醉意，呵。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:169
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My friend, you deserve it. Without their saurian allies Clan Blackcrest is "
"on the run, and Clan Whitefang is falling back out of the eastern hills."
msgstr ""
"挚友，你当之无愧。若无蜥蜴人的援手，黑牙氏族早已溃逃，而白牙氏族也正从东部山"
"岭后撤。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:173
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At long last lift the shadows of war; the realm is finally at peace. "
"Perchance the coming days will bring laughter to the streets of Weldyn once "
"again."
msgstr ""
"战火终已消散；王国终得和平。或许，未来的日子里，韦德林（Weldyn）的街头将再次"
"回荡着欢声笑语。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:177
#, fuzzy
msgid "For the first time in a long time, all is finally well with the world."
msgstr "长夜终逝，万物归序，这方世界终于重获安宁。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:223
#, fuzzy
msgid "(<i>Yawn</i>)"
msgstr "（哈欠）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:227
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ugh, what a headache. I shouldn’t have drunk so much... now nature calls."
msgstr "哎呀，这头痛欲裂。我不该喝那么多……现在，身体有些许呼唤了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador's woken up in the middle of the night to go use the latrines
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:243
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Disgusting. Alduin really needs to invent a spell for cleaning latrines.\n"
"\n"
"Mayhaps as High Advisor I can finally get someone to research that... "
"(<i>yawn</i>)"
msgstr ""
"真是令人作呕。奥渡因真该发明一种清理厕所的咒语……\n"
"\n"
"或许身为最高顾问，我总算能有人去钻研这项伟业了……（打哈欠）"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:265
msgid "Oh!"
msgstr "哦！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:269
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You have startled me, Your Majesty. The darkest hour of night is hardly a "
"queenly time to be about — should you not be asleep with Garard? ’tis not "
"every day that Wesnoth wins a war."
msgstr ""
"陛下，您吓到我了。夜色最浓重之时，并非君王该现身之际——您不该与伽拉德一同安寝"
"吗？毕竟，韦诺王国并非日日都能赢得战争。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:274
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hello Delfador — or should I say, “Delfador the Great.”"
msgstr "你好，德法多——或者说，我该称您“德法多大师”吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:278
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Such pleasure to once more speak with my husband’s famous right hand. I "
"never did properly thank you for returning me back to him, all those years "
"ago."
msgstr ""
"能再次与我丈夫那位大名鼎鼎的左膀右臂交谈，真是一大乐事。多年前，您将我送回他"
"身边，我始终未能好好道谢。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:286
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re a powerful man, a <i>dangerous</i> man, Delfador. I pity the fool who "
"finds themselves on the wrong end of your staff... yet I oft pity even more "
"so the fool who rules behind it, so consumed by the minutiae of war."
msgstr ""
"你是一位强权之人，一位<em>危险</em>之人，德法多大师。我同情那些误入你法杖锋芒"
"下的愚者……然而，我往往更同情那位凌驾于其上的君主——那位被战争的细枝末节彻底吞"
"噬的愚者。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:291
#, fuzzy
msgid "Err... I’m not sure I follow, Your Highness—"
msgstr "呃……殿下，恕我不太明白您的意思——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:304
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"What’s going on here? Careful, Delfador — don’t believe a word she says."
msgstr "这里究竟发生了什么？小心，德法多大师——她说的话，一个字都别信。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:308
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Woman, are you not satisfied with my son; you must have my wizard too!? Away "
"with you, wench, and save your lacquered tongue for another day!"
msgstr ""
"女人，难道我儿子的陪衬还不足以让你满足，你还要抢走我的法师不成？滚开，你这贱"
"婢，把你那油滑的巧舌留给明天再施展吧！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:312
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Peace, peace! Wesnoth stands triumphant; there’s no need for quarreling!"
msgstr ""
"和平！和平！韦诺王国已 triumphantly 屹立，无需再争执！平静，平静！韦诺王国已"
"巍然屹立，大获全胜；何必再起争执！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:316
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It’s quite all right, Delfador; I take no offense at my husband’s cruel "
"words. Far be it from me to interfere in military matters — the king and his "
"new advisor have doubtless much to speak on. I graciously take my leave."
msgstr ""
"无妨，德法多；对于我丈夫那残酷的言语，我毫不在意。我绝无干扰军务之心——国王与"
"他的新谋士想必有诸多要务需商议。容我恭敬告退。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:329
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That seemed a little extreme, m’lord! Surely a little politeness would not "
"go amiss, especially with regards to your own blood! I’ve heard nothing but "
"praise for the queen from most of the court."
msgstr ""
"这似乎有些过激了，尊贵的老爷！些许礼貌想必无伤大雅，尤其是面对您的血脉至亲"
"时！我从宫廷众人那里听到的，对王后全是溢美之词。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:333
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They don’t know her. You don’t know her. All is not well with my family, "
"Delfador."
msgstr "他们并不了解她，你也不了解。德法多，我家中已非昔日光景，局势危急。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:342
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My ancestors — the first king and the first queen — led the entire race of "
"men across the ocean to found Wesnoth. Those two understood each other. They "
"saved us all from the terrors of the west. They raised a strong prince, a "
"good son."
msgstr ""
"我的祖先——第一任国王与第一任王后——率领全体人类跨越重洋，建立了韦诺王国。那两"
"人彼此心意相通，他们使我们免于西方的恐怖。他们抚养出了一位强韧的王子，一位贤"
"良的嗣君。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:346
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And what of I? This ruinous war, just to satisfy my own ambition? All was "
"nearly lost. Without your magic, all might have been. I’ve made so many "
"mistakes, my friend."
msgstr ""
"我该如何自处？这场毁天灭地的战争，难道仅为了成全我的一己私欲？一切几近覆灭。"
"若无你们的魔法，后果不堪设想。我的朋友，我犯下的错，实在太多了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:354
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"No man is without flaws, Your Highness. Certainly not you and I. But I’ve "
"followed you through thick and thin, and together we have always emerged "
"triumphant."
msgstr ""
"陛下，人无完人，您与我皆不例外。但我始终追随您左右，风雨同舟，而我们也总能携"
"手凯旋。"

#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:383
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:336
msgid "Father."
msgstr "父亲。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:388
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Boy? This is a pleasant surprise; I thought you were with your uncle, "
"guarding Fort Garard. Come to celebrate the war’s end with us, did you? It "
"is good to see you again."
msgstr ""
"“小子？这可是个意外的惊喜。原以为你正陪着你叔叔，在伽拉德堡守城。怎么，是特意"
"来同我们一道庆祝战争结束的？再次见到你，甚好。”"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:394
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hold on, what’s the matter with— you’re <b><i>injured</i></b>!? What "
"happened! Where’s that useless Methor when you need him?!"
msgstr ""
"且慢，怎么了——你 <b><i>受伤</i></b> 了？！究竟发生了何事！梅瑟在你最需要他的"
"时候竟不在场吗，那个废物！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:402
#, fuzzy
msgid "It’s about your—"
msgstr "是关于你——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:410
msgid "...Father, it’s Uncle. Prince Arand."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#. Eldred doesn’t show a lot of emotion here. He's lying, and not very good at it
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:416
msgid ""
"He’s found the Sceptre of Fire. He declared his claim to the throne, and "
"seized control of Fort Garard. My bodyguards and I tried to stop him, but we "
"didn’t even get close. I barely made it out alive."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:420
#, fuzzy
msgid "Arand tried to kill me, Father. He’s coming for you next."
msgstr "父亲，阿兰德曾企图弑杀于我。下一步，他就要来对付您了。"

#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:426
msgid "Garard—?"
msgstr "伽拉德——？"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:430
msgid "WHAT!?"
msgstr "什么！？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:440
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That TREASONOUS son-of-a, son-of— I knew something felt suspicious lately."
msgstr "那个卖国的畜生……不，该死的畜生！我就觉得最近有些不对劲。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:444
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It all makes sense now. Arand is my spymaster — of course the spies told me "
"nothing. And Arand warned me that others were searching for the Sceptre... "
"to trick me into sending away Lionel, my most loyal general!"
msgstr ""
"如今一切豁然开朗。阿兰德乃我的密探总管——难怪那些探子对我缄口不言。阿兰德曾警"
"告我，有人正搜寻圣火权杖……其意在诱骗我遣走莱昂内尔，那是我麾下最忠诚的将军！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:449
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"How DARE he threaten me? How dare he lay a FINGER on my son? I’ll see him "
"hang for this."
msgstr "他竟敢威胁我？竟敢用一根手指碰我的儿子？我定要将他绞死以正法！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:453
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, take command of the cavalry; my personal royal cavalry — they’re "
"the only ones I still trust. Ride to Fort Garard and burn it to the ground!"
msgstr ""
"德法多，你率领骑兵部队；我的私人皇家禁卫军——他们是我如今仅存的信任。直扑加拉"
"德要塞，将其付之一炬！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:457
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I want every one of those traitors dead! Return with Arand’s head— his HEAD! "
"Or don’t return at all. Do you understand!?"
msgstr ""
"我要那些叛徒全部毙命！带着阿兰德的脑袋回来——**他的脑袋**！否则就别回来了。你"
"明白吗！？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:461
#, fuzzy
msgid "Yes, Your Majesty!"
msgstr "谨遵圣裁，陛下！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:477
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, I couldn’t help but overhear. Prince Arand, the king’s brother?? "
"That can’t be."
msgstr "德法多，我不小心听到了。阿兰德亲王，是国王的兄弟？这绝不可能。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:481
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The young Prince Eldred’s wounds are clear as day, Deoran. Will you ride "
"with us? Every moment we delay is another chance for Arand to rally more "
"rebels to his cause."
msgstr ""
"年轻的埃雷德王子的伤口清晰可见，德欧兰。你愿与我们同行吗？每一刻的拖延，都是"
"阿兰德招揽更多叛军投奔他麾下的良机。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:485
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But a sentence of death, without even trial? Arand is thoughtful and quiet, "
"and not known to be ambitious."
msgstr ""
"但竟是一纸死刑，连庭审都未曾给予？阿兰德生性思虑深远、沉郁寡言，世人从未听说"
"他怀有野心。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. this mirrors Methor's request to Lionel in S10x
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:490
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The king has commanded his death, yes. But you are the one sent to carry it "
"out. You don’t... <b><i>have</i></b> to go, you know. At least not so "
"hastily."
msgstr ""
"国王确实下令处死他。但派你去执行的人，是你自己。你……未必<b><i>必须</i></b>现"
"在就动身，你明白的。至少，不必如此仓促。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:494
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Refuse Garard’s order. Hold back, dispatch scouts, and gather more "
"information before committing so much of the army to this attack. Wesnoth "
"can scant afford a civil war, and certainly not so soon after the orcs!"
msgstr ""
"莫从伽拉德的命令行事。暂且按兵不动，先派遣斥候，搜集更多情报，切勿在此时贸然"
"将大军投入此役。韦诺王国已无力再承受一场内战，尤其在兽人战祸方休之际，更是万"
"万不可！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:498
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Are you mad?! It’s neither your place nor mine to second-guess His Majesty. "
"Especially not now, when he needs loyalty more than ever."
msgstr ""
"你疯了吗？！质疑陛下的英明绝非你我该为，尤其在此时，他比以往任何时候都更需要"
"忠诚。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:502
#, fuzzy
msgid "Delfador, I really worry—"
msgstr "德法多大师，我深感忧虑——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:506
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And... besides, I’ve lived half my life fighting alongside the king, "
"fighting to gain his favor. Today I’m “The Great”, but I didn’t even have a "
"name before I first began to battle."
msgstr ""
"而且……况且，我已大半生与国王并肩作战，竭力赢得他的青睐。今日我虽被称"
"为“大”师，但在我初次披甲上阵之前，却连个名字都无。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:510
#, fuzzy
msgid "Without that, who am I? I don’t want to end up exiled, like you were..."
msgstr "若失去它，我又是谁？我不愿落得和你一样的下场……被流放。"

#. [unit]: type=Knight, id=Kaylan
#. [event]: id=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:523
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:408
msgid "Sir Kaylan"
msgstr "凯兰爵士"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/11x_Revelry.cfg:542
#, fuzzy
msgid "Royal cavalry, form up on me! We go at once!"
msgstr "皇家骑兵，随我列阵！即刻出发！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=12_The_Traitor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:13
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Traitor"
msgstr "叛徒"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:32
#, fuzzy
msgid "Royal Cavalry"
msgstr "皇家骑兵"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Halberdier, id=Luraery
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:61
#, fuzzy
msgid "Luraery"
msgstr "露拉瑞"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]: type=Lieutenant, id=Aelyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:80
msgid "Aelyn"
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:284
#, fuzzy
msgid "Fall back! Hold the walls, protect the fort!"
msgstr "后撤！死守城墙，保全堡垒！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:364
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The scouts bring grim news — a fearsome army rides against us! Long have I "
"dreaded this moment. Rally together, fight as one, and we will assuredly "
"triumph in the coming civil war!"
msgstr ""
"斥候送来了令人忧惧的消息——一支令人胆寒的大军正朝我们杀来！我早已预料到这一时"
"刻。众人集结，万众一心，必将在即将到来的内战中凯旋！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:390
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Curses, we have already been spotted. Time is of the essence; we must strike "
"before Arand can turn more Wesnothians to his cause!"
msgstr ""
"糟了，我们已经被发现了！刻不容缓，必须在阿兰德将更多韦诺人拉入他的阵营之前，"
"先发制人！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:426
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The king’s personal cavalry stands at your command, great Delfador! Direct "
"us as you will, and the traitor prince shall fall beneath our hooves!"
msgstr ""
"国王亲卫骑兵团此刻皆听您调遣，伟大的德法多大师！请随您心意指挥，那叛变的王子"
"必将在我们的蹄下灭亡！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:434
#, fuzzy
msgid "Defeat Prince Arand"
msgstr "击败亲王阿兰德"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:456
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your veteran soldiers have been left behind with Deoran <b>(you’ll see them "
"again next scenario)</b>, but you can instead recruit Cavalrymen and "
"Horsemen!\n"
"\n"
"Cavalrymen are general-purpose mounted infantry, with moderate damage for a "
"moderate price. Horsemen are more expensive, but their risky charge attack "
"deals heavy damage."
msgstr ""
"您的老兵们已暂留在德欧兰处 <b>（将在下一场景与您重逢）</b>，但您此刻可招募骑"
"兵与骑士！\n"
"\n"
"骑兵是用途广泛的骑马步兵，以适中的代价换取适中的伤害。骑士造价更高，其高风险"
"的冲锋攻击却能造成毁灭性打击。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:462
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Garard’s Royal Cavalry are loyal and skilled, but neither Horsemen nor "
"Cavalrymen are well-suited for fighting Arand’s army of Spearmen and "
"Pikemen. My magic shall have to make up the difference."
msgstr ""
"伽拉德的皇家骑兵忠诚且技艺精湛，然而无论是骑士还是骑兵，面对阿兰德统率的长矛"
"兵与戟兵方阵，都难以适应战场。唯有我的魔法能弥补这巨大的差距。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:466
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If only my outlaws and veterans could have marched fast enough to keep up. "
"If the king’s own brother is a usurper, who in Wesnoth can I really trust?"
msgstr ""
"若我的流亡者与老兵能行军得再快些，赶上大军该多好。既然国王亲弟皆已成篡位者，"
"这韦诺境内，我又该真正信任何人？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male cavalryman or horseman
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:480
#, fuzzy
msgid "Fight on without me, friends! Fight for our king!"
msgstr "无需我陪同，诸位挚友，继续奋战！为了我们的君王，战斗吧！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:492
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There’s right where I’d stood, back when I fought my first real battle. How "
"simple everything seemed back then..."
msgstr ""
"此处正是我当年首次投身真实战场的立足之地。那时的世界，显得多么简单纯粹……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:504
#, fuzzy
msgid "Welcome to Garard’s Wold, last civilized town north of the Great River."
msgstr "欢迎来到伽拉德的沃德，这里是泰河以北最后一座文明城镇。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:526
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Such devastation. Garard ordered us to “burn it to the ground”, and we did..."
msgstr "如此劫难。伽拉德曾下令“将其夷为平地”，我们……确实照做了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:560
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The rebellion is broken! In the name of King Garard and the royal scepter, I "
"strike you down!"
msgstr "叛乱已被粉碎！奉加拉德国王与圣火权杖之名，我宣判你败亡！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:565
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"King Garard?! My brother sent you? But I thought—? Wait, stop, please, I "
"don’t understand!"
msgstr ""
"加拉德国王？！我的兄长派您前来？可我以为……？且慢，请住手，我……我不明白！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:578
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The young Prince Eldred told us how you tried to claim the throne for "
"yourself, Arand. You are mortally wounded — confess now, and King Garard may "
"forgive you in death."
msgstr ""
"年轻的埃雷德王子曾告诉我们，你妄图为王位，阿兰德。你已身受致命重伤——此刻招"
"供，或许国王伽拉德会在你死后宽恕你。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:582
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By the Sceptre, I swear I have never conspired against my brother Garard. "
"Eldred is the traitor! Eldred and Asheviere are the traitors, not me!"
msgstr ""
"以圣火权杖之名，我起誓从未与兄长伽拉德为敌！真正叛徒是埃雷德！埃雷德与艾什薇"
"尔才是叛徒，而非我！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:591
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My life runs short; you must believe my tale. For some time now my spies "
"have heard whispers of a terrible conspiracy, a plot to overthrow the very "
"king himself.\n"
"\n"
"’Twas not a fortnight hence that my suspicions were confirmed — I gained "
"incontrovertible evidence proving the chief conspirators to be none other "
"than the queen and the prince, two of my brother’s closest companions!"
msgstr ""
"吾命将尽，务必信我之言。近来，我的斥候屡有传闻，言及一场惊天阴谋——旨在推翻君"
"王本身。\n"
"\n"
"并非过了一两旬，我的疑心便得以确证——我获取了无可辩驳的铁证，证明主谋竟正是王"
"后与王子，我那兄长最亲密的两位至交！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:597
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yet no sooner did this news arrive than my bodyguards and I were set upon by "
"Eldred himself, so bold as to strike even during the day!\n"
"\n"
"I slew several of his fighters and grievously wounded the young prince, yet "
"barely escaped to Fort Garard before my guards were overwhelmed."
msgstr ""
"然而，消息刚传至，我与我的护卫便遭艾雷德亲自突袭，竟如此大胆，白日之中便敢动"
"手！\n"
"\n"
"我斩杀了其数名家臣，并将那年轻王子重创，但在护卫们被淹没之前，我唯有勉强突围"
"至伽拉德堡垒。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:603
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And now it seems that Eldred has found a way to finish me off after all..."
msgstr "看来，埃雷德终究找到了终结我的办法……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:608
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I sense the ring of truth in your words... But if what you say is true, why "
"fight when we approached instead of surrender? To my eyes, your resistance "
"only sealed your guilt."
msgstr ""
"我嗅到了你言辞中的真理之环……但倘若你所言属实，为何在我们兵临城下之时，你们不"
"选择投降，而是选择抗争？在我眼中，你们的抵抗反倒坐实了自身的罪责。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:613
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Can you blame me? Rolling waves of mud smashing my fortress to bits — I "
"thought this some foul magic of the queen’s, here to finish what Eldred "
"failed to do! For many months now have I suspected the influence of a "
"necromancer most powerful..."
msgstr ""
"你又怎能怪我？翻滚的泥浆巨浪将我的堡垒撕成碎片——我曾以为这是王后施展的邪恶魔"
"法，意图彻底完成埃雷德未竟的事业！数月来，我便一直怀疑有一位法力通天的死灵法"
"师在幕后操纵……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:620
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Can you blame me? Rolling waves of fire burning my fortress to cinders — I "
"thought this some foul magic of the queen’s, here to finish what Eldred "
"failed to do! For many months now have I suspected the influence of a "
"necromancer most powerful..."
msgstr ""
"你又怎能怪我？火焰如狂涛般席卷，将我的要塞化为焦土——我本以为这是王后施展的邪"
"恶魔法，旨在彻底完成埃雷德未尽的罪恶！其实，数月来我便早已察觉，有一股极为强"
"大的死灵法师之力量在暗中作祟……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:627
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Can you blame me? I thought your cavalry and magic to be more of the same — "
"servants of the queen, here to finish what Eldred failed to do! For many "
"months now have I suspected the influence of a necromancer most powerful..."
msgstr ""
"你怪得了我吗？我曾以为你的骑兵与魔法不过是老一套——皆是王后的爪牙，前来替埃雷"
"德完成那未竟之事！实则数月以来，我便已察觉一股至强死灵法师的阴影笼罩……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:633
#, fuzzy
msgid "Malal. He is dead now."
msgstr "玛拉尔。如今他已伏诛。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:637
#, fuzzy
msgid "But if you are here with me, then Eldred is alone with the king?"
msgstr "但若您与我同在，那埃雷德是否便与国王独处了？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:652
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"So much blood... please, you must believe me! Save my brother... save "
"Wesnoth..."
msgstr "如此多的鲜血……求你了，请相信我！救救我的兄长……拯救韦诺王国……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:695
#, fuzzy
msgid "Prince Eldred? What are you doing here?"
msgstr "埃雷德王子？您在此做什么？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:705
#, fuzzy
msgid "There he is! Get him!"
msgstr "就在那儿！拿下他！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:713
#, fuzzy
msgid "Huh? Wha—"
msgstr "唔？什——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=13_Revelry_Revisited
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:26
#, fuzzy
msgid "Revelry, Revisited"
msgstr "再临的狂欢"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:45
#, fuzzy
msgid "Deoran’s Company"
msgstr "德欧兰的部队"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=13_Revelry_Revisited
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:80
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sir Johan"
msgstr "约翰爵士"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=13_Revelry_Revisited
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:81
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sir Grey"
msgstr "灰爵士"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [scenario]: id=13_Revelry_Revisited
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:82
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sir Gwido"
msgstr "吉多爵士"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:160
#, fuzzy
msgid "I’ve pillaged $gold_pickup gold from Eldred’s treasury!"
msgstr "我从埃雷德的国库中掠夺了 $gold_pickup 的金币！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:279
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:283
#, fuzzy
msgid "So."
msgstr "如此。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:291
#, fuzzy
msgid "Guess you’re the boss now."
msgstr "看来现在你当家作主了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:295
#, fuzzy
msgid "It would seem as such. Would that Delfador had stayed."
msgstr "看来确实如此。但愿德法多大师能留驻此地。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:301
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...hey, is it true that you’ve lived with elves? I hear they’re the greatest "
"bestest most beautifulest creatures there are!"
msgstr ""
"……嘿，听说你和精灵住在一起？这该不会是真的吧？我常听人说，他们是世间最伟大、"
"最棒、最美不胜收的生灵呢！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:302
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"female^...hey, is it true that you’ve lived with elves? I hear they’re the "
"greatest bestest most beautifulest creatures there are!"
msgstr ""
"女^……嘿，真的吗？你曾和精灵住在一起？我听说他们是世上最伟大、最美好、最美得无"
"法形容的生物！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. referencing the events of TSG
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:307
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Elves? No. Be not fooled by a pretty face — I have seen even the noblest "
"elven sage corrupted to such darkness as to rival the foulest human or orc."
msgstr ""
"精灵？绝非如此。切莫被那张美丽的面容所蒙蔽——我曾亲眼目睹，即便是最德高望重的"
"精灵智者，亦会被腐化为至深的黑暗，其行径之邪恶，足以令最卑劣的人类或兽人望尘"
"莫及。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:311
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Although, I suppose there is at least one young elf of my acquaintance to "
"whom I might ascribe such virtues. My thoughts find her often, in these dark "
"times."
msgstr ""
"虽然，依我之见，我认识的一位年轻精灵或许也配得上这些美德。在这黑暗岁月里，她"
"常萦绕于我的思绪之中。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Kestrel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:330
#, fuzzy
msgid "Sir, Delfador and the Royal Cavalry are out of sight."
msgstr "大人，德法多大师与皇家骑兵已消失在视野之中。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:340
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All healed up? Excellent. Come out of the rain and join me in my tent. We’ll "
"soon put this rebellion to rest."
msgstr ""
"全好了？太棒了。别在雨里待着了，进我的帐篷来。咱们很快就能平息这场叛乱。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:346
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I admit, I was worried about you, son. <i>“Soft”</i> I thought — if I should "
"fall, could you truly lead our people to victory? I wanted to toughen you up."
msgstr ""
"我承认，我曾为你担忧，孩子。<i>“软弱”</i>我曾心想——若我身陷险境，你是否真能带"
"领我们走向胜利？我本想让你变得更强韧。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. I think this is the only time Garard actually calls Eldred by his name. Not "boy" or "son"
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:351
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But now? Sniffing out treachery in our own family? Taking it upon yourself "
"to bring Arand to justice! You may have failed to defeat him, but failure "
"does not diminish the trying. You did well today, Eldred."
msgstr ""
"但如今？竟要在我族内部嗅探奸佞？擅自将你兄长阿兰德绳之以法！你虽未能将其击"
"败，但那份尝试本身，已足以彰显你的价值。今日之举，你做得很好，埃雷德。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:377
#, fuzzy
msgid "(shocked) You—"
msgstr "（震惊）你——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:397
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1018
#, fuzzy
msgid "Finally."
msgstr "终于。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:407
#, fuzzy
msgid "Wake! Alarm—"
msgstr "醒醒！警报——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:411
#, fuzzy
msgid "(gulp, deep breath)"
msgstr "（深吸一口气）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:423
#, fuzzy
msgid "WAKE! ALARM! DEORAN HAS SLAIN THE KING!"
msgstr "醒来！警报！德欧兰弑君！"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:428
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "什么！？"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:434
msgid ""
"Garard truly is dead, and by the sword at that! Eldred was the last to "
"enter..."
msgstr "伽拉德确已死去，且是死于剑下！埃雷德是最后进入的人……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:438
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"See Deoran there, standing now at the mouth of my father’s tent? He strikes "
"in cold blood, at the height of my father’s triumph! He takes revenge for "
"his long years of exile! Only a heart shaped by hate and twisted by elves "
"could commit such a foul deed!"
msgstr ""
"看着那边的德欧兰，此刻正伫立在我父亲的帐篷口！他竟在父亲荣耀登顶之时，冷血行"
"凶！这是对他多年流亡生涯的报复！唯有那颗被仇恨塑造、又被精灵扭曲的心，才做得"
"出如此卑劣的勾当！"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:442
msgid "No! Eldred is—"
msgstr "不！埃雷德他——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=eldred4
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:446
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Calamity! The ambassador always seemed so polite! How could he do this? How "
"could we let him do this?!"
msgstr ""
"大难！那位大使向来显得彬彬有礼！他怎能行此大逆之事？我们又怎能容许他如此作"
"为？！"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:450
msgid "No! I—"
msgstr "不！我——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=eldred3
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:454
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We all know that Deoran was not loved by the king. All this while he must "
"have been biding his time, plotting his attack! And look, that outlaw of "
"Delfador’s stands beside him, witness and accomplice to the crime!"
msgstr ""
"众人都知晓，德欧兰从未得国王欢心。他这些年必定是在隐忍待时，图谋此次袭击！且"
"看，德法多大师那个通缉在逃的党羽正伫立其侧，乃是此桩罪行的见证者与同谋！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:459
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"No, no! $companion_name is not my accomplice— I mean, neither of us are "
"accomplices— that is to say—"
msgstr ""
"不，不！$companion_name 并非我的同谋——我是说，我们俩都绝不是同谋——我的意思是"
"——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:468
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ignore the killer’s murderous ramblings. Rally, soldiers of Wesnoth! Slay "
"Deoran and avenge the king!"
msgstr "休听那杀手的狂言乱语。集结吧，韦诺的勇士们！杀了德欧兰，为国王复仇！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:500
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(aghast) Horrors below, Garard’s own son; what has happened to my beautiful "
"kingdom? How—"
msgstr ""
"(惊骇) 泰河之下竟有如此恐怖之事，竟是伽拉德亲王亲生的孽种！我美丽的王国究竟遭"
"逢了什么劫难？如何——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:504
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I don’t— what do I do? They all believe Eldred!? I’m not ready for a fight!"
msgstr "我——我能做什么？他们全都相信埃雷德！？我还没准备好战斗！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:509
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Listen boss, I’m not much for politics, but I know when to run and that’s "
"now! We’ve got to get out of here!"
msgstr ""
"听好了，老大！我可不是什么政治高手，但我知道什么时候该跑——就是现在！咱们得赶"
"紧离开这儿！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:510
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"female^Listen boss, I’m not much for politics, but I know when to run and "
"that’s now! We’ve got to get out of here!"
msgstr ""
"女^听着，首领，我不太懂政治，但我知道何时该逃，而此刻便是最好时机！我们必须立"
"刻离开此地！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:514
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I— yes, you’re right! With Garard dead, Delfador commands the greatest "
"honest force left in Wesnoth, and he has no idea what has just transpired! "
"Delfador must be warned."
msgstr ""
"我——是的，你说得对！伽拉德已死，德法多大师掌握着韦诺王国仅存的、最诚实的军"
"队，而他对此事竟毫不知情！必须立刻告知德法多！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:518
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If we are lucky, we may yet be able to save Arand from Delfador’s ill-"
"informed assault. But even barring that, Delfador’s leadership can surely "
"rally enough soldiers to oppose Eldred by force of arms!\n"
"\n"
"$companion_name, go, now! Slip away along the eastern road!"
msgstr ""
"若上天眷顾，我们或许尚能救下阿兰德，免遭德法多那鲁莽的冒进所伤。但即便退一"
"步，德法多的统领也定能集结足够兵力，以武力抗衡埃雷德！\n"
"\n"
"$companion_name，走！立刻！沿东道悄然撤离！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:529
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"...hey, how come you’re not following? Don’t even think about sacrificing "
"yourself because of “chivalry” or some other bunk."
msgstr "……嘿，你怎会不跟上？可别想着为了什么“骑士精神”或是别的胡扯而牺牲自己。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:533
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Nothing so heroic. Wesnoth’s forces may believe me a conspirator now, but I "
"will not give up on them so easily. If I fight my way into a private "
"audience with each leader I’m sure I can make them see the truth about "
"Eldred — Garard’s poor family relationships were no secret.\n"
"\n"
"Even if I can but convince commanders to delay their support for the traitor "
"prince, that will give Delfador and me much-needed time to gather gold "
"before our next battle!"
msgstr ""
"谈不上什么英雄壮举。韦诺的军队此刻或许视我为阴谋家，但我绝不会轻易放弃他们。"
"若能通过一番搏杀，争取到与每位领袖单独会面的机会，我确信定能让他们看清埃雷德"
"的真相——伽拉德那糟糕的家世纠葛，向来不是什么秘密。\n"
"\n"
"即便我只能说服各位指挥官暂缓向那位叛国王子提供支持，也足以让德法多和我赢得宝"
"贵的时间，在下一场大战前积聚所需的金币！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:539
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<i>Defeating enemy leaders will increase your starting gold in the next "
"scenario.</i>"
msgstr "击败敌方首领将使您在下一场战役中获得更多的起始金币。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:543
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When at last my strength is spent, I will flee through the forest — my steed "
"is elf-stock, and no rival bred in Wesnoth can outpace its haste amongst the "
"trees. But the more support I can garner now, the better our position will "
"be in the future!"
msgstr ""
"待我力竭之时，我便会遁入密林——我的坐骑源自精灵血脉，凡韦诺所产之马，纵有千般"
"神骏，亦无法在树丛间与之争逐。然而，此刻若能多邀得一分援手，吾等未来的局势便"
"多一分胜算！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:547
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Now make haste, and godspeed! You must reunite with Delfador; I will send "
"what soldiers I can spare after you!"
msgstr ""
"此刻务必速行，愿天助汝！你须与德法多大师重聚，我将派遣所能调遣的援军随后跟"
"进！"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:555
msgid "Avenge the king! Don’t let them escape!"
msgstr "为国王复仇！绝不可让他们逃走！"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:596
msgid "$gold_pickup gold"
msgstr "$gold_pickup 金币"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:611
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Defeat as many enemy leaders as possible before Deoran is defeated\n"
"    <i>(each defeated leader yields bonus gold in the next scenario)</i>"
msgstr ""
"在德欧兰被击败前，尽可能击败更多的敌方首领\n"
"（每击败一位首领，下一战役中将获得额外金币奖励）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#. $|escape_turns_remaining is probably between 0 and 10
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:618
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Evacuate veteran units along the eastern road ($|escape_turns_remaining "
"turns remaining)"
msgstr "沿东线公路撤退老兵单位（剩余 |escape_turns_remaining 回合）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:625
#, fuzzy
msgid "When an enemy leader is defeated, their remaining soldiers will flee."
msgstr "当敌方首领被击败，其残部将四散奔逃。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [note]: description=<b>
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:629
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1089
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1244
#, fuzzy
msgid "This is the second-to-last scenario."
msgstr "这是倒数第二个场景。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:656
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Units that escape to the east will be available to recall in the next "
"scenario, but units that do not escape will be lost (either scattered or "
"killed) — including units on your recall list! The eastern path will remain "
"open until the end of turn 7.\n"
"\n"
"You should evacuate enough veterans to have a strong recall list next "
"scenario, but also defeat enough enemy leaders so that you’ll have gold for "
"recalling."
msgstr ""
"任何向东突围的部队将可在下一关中重新召回，未能突围者（无论散佚或被歼）都将永"
"久损失——包括您召回列表中的部队！向东的通路将保持开放，直至第 {ESCAPE_TURNS} "
"回合结束。\n"
"\n"
"您应疏散足够多的精锐老兵，以便在下一关中拥有强大的召回阵容；同时，也需击败足"
"够的敌方首领，以积累召唤部队所需的黄金。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:685
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fleeing too quickly will only seal my guilt in the eyes of Wesnoth’s "
"commanders. I do not intend to run until I have no other choice!"
msgstr ""
"仓皇而逃，只会让韦诺的将领们认定我罪责难逃。我绝不会逃，直到万不得已之时！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:699
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I hear orc-drums approaching the eastern road! Any more who wish to flee — "
"now is your last chance."
msgstr "我听见兽人的战鼓已逼近东大路！若有谁执意逃亡——此刻便是最后的机会。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:704
#, fuzzy
msgid "I hear orc-drums approaching the eastern road! Our time runs short."
msgstr "我听见鼓声从东边大道逼近！留给我们的时间不多了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:730
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1103
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You will now start the next scenario with $bonus_gold total gold (plus "
"$s11_carryover carryover from Delfador)"
msgstr ""
"您即将开始下一场战役，初始金币为 $bonus_gold（另加德法多所带遗产 "
"$s11_carryover）。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:735
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1108
#, fuzzy
msgid "You will now start the next scenario with $bonus_gold total gold!"
msgstr "你即将开始下一战役，并携带总计 $bonus_gold 枚金币！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:751
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"One leader is defeated. I had hoped to gain a new ally, but depriving Eldred "
"and buying time is good enough. And now that this keep is ours, I can "
"recruit more soldiers to aid in the fight."
msgstr ""
"一位首领已被击败。我本希望能赢得一位新的盟友，但剥夺埃雷德的势力并为他争取时"
"间，已属万幸。如今这座堡垒已落入我们手中，我便能招募更多士兵，助我们一臂之"
"力。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:756
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"One leader is defeated. I had hoped to gain a new ally, but depriving Eldred "
"and buying time is good enough."
msgstr ""
"一位领袖已被击败。我本期望能赢得一位新盟友，但剥夺埃雷德的势力并换取时间，已"
"足以让人欣慰。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:761
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I should remember — soldiers I evacuate east will be available to fight "
"Eldred later, but if I evacuate too many I will be too weak to fight "
"effectively here!"
msgstr ""
"我须谨记——若向东撤退的士兵日后能助战埃雷德，固是幸事；但若撤走过多，此地战力"
"必遭削弱，届时恐难成事！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. tell the player that this isn't the entirety of Wesnoth’s army. Even if the player defeats most of them here, Eldred will still have a big army in the next (and final) scenario.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:771
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran’s putting up a real fight! But even if he defeats me, he’ll never get "
"back into Wesnoth — we still have soldiers encamped on the southern shore."
msgstr ""
"德欧兰正在殊死搏斗！但即便他胜过了我，也无法重返韦诺——我们仍有军队驻扎在南"
"岸。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:785
#, fuzzy
msgid "So much ill will... The captains of old would have died for their king."
msgstr "如此多的恶念……昔日的那些统帅，早已愿为君王赴死。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:789
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Perhaps it is not a coincidence that so many of the old guard fell in battle "
"against the orcs."
msgstr "或许，旧日守御者在对兽人的战场上纷纷陨落，并非偶然。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:801
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You are defeated, mage! Lend me your ear and hear the truth about Garard’s "
"death! ’twas not I who struck the blow, but Prince Eldred!"
msgstr ""
"你已败亡，法师！且听我言，细闻伽拉德之死的真相！挥下致命一击者并非我，而是埃"
"雷德亲王！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Red Mage or Silver Mage
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:806
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’m not stupid, Deoran; I’ve heard the whispers about how Asheviere is "
"raising her son. But isn’t it all for the best? Garard wasn’t going to give "
"up warmongering until we were all dead; at least this way maybe I can get "
"back to Alduin in one piece!"
msgstr ""
"我可没那么蠢，德欧兰；关于艾什薇尔如何抚养她儿子，那些流言我早听腻了。但这一"
"切，难道不是皆大欢喜吗？伽拉德若不让所有人血流成河、战死沙场，绝不会停止他的"
"好战行径；至少如今这般，我还能平安重返奥渡因！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:816
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You care so little for the affairs of Wesnoth? Then go; lead your magi home, "
"and trouble the mainland no more."
msgstr ""
"你竟对韦诺王国的事务如此漠不关心？那便去吧；率领你的法师们归家，从此不要再在"
"陆地上兴风作浪了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:822
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You care so little for the affairs of Wesnoth? Then go; return home to "
"Alduin, and trouble the mainland no more."
msgstr ""
"你竟对韦诺王国的政事如此漠不关心？那便请回；回到奥渡因去吧，从此别再在大陆上"
"兴风作浪。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:843
#, fuzzy
msgid "You—"
msgstr "你——"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Shock Trooper
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:848
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Don’t even start. Garard dragged me away from my life of luxury to be an "
"officer in his lousy war. I always wanted him dead, and I’m glad someone "
"finally built up the courage to do it."
msgstr ""
"别费口舌了。伽拉德硬是把那个享受奢华生活的我给拽走，扔进他这破仗里当什么军"
"官。我早就巴不得他死，现在看到有人终于鼓起勇气杀了他，我倒觉得痛快。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Shock Trooper
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:853
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Kill me if you must, but I’ll never condemn the prince’s actions. From what "
"I hear, Garard was a pretty lousy father and husband too. Now am I free to "
"go, or not?"
msgstr ""
"要杀便杀吧，但我绝不会诋毁王子的所作所为。据我所闻，伽拉德既是个蹩脚的父亲，"
"也是个糟糕的丈夫。那么，现在我可以走了吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Shock Trooper
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:862
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That’s what I thought. Now get out of my way — my men and I are going back "
"home to Weldyn."
msgstr "果然如此。现在给我让开——我和我的部下要回温尔丁（Weldyn）去了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:881
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Colonel! You’re a man of experience, and a man of wisdom. Do you not care "
"for your king? Do you truly believe that it was by my hand he fell?"
msgstr ""
"上校！您是一位经验丰富且深谙智慧之人。您难道不在乎您的国王吗？您真的相信是他"
"被我亲手所杀吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male General
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:886
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I cared for Garard, but I care even more for the soldiers and common folk of "
"Wesnoth, folk who have just been plunged into civil war."
msgstr ""
"我虽曾关怀伽拉德，但我更关切韦诺的将士与百姓。这些子民，方才骤然卷入内战的深"
"渊。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male General
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:891
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Whether the deed was done by your hand or Eldred’s, it is my duty as a "
"commander to end the fighting as swiftly as possible. And that means "
"crushing your revolt."
msgstr ""
"无论这暴行出自你手，还是埃雷德所为，作为一名统帅，我的职责便是尽快平息战火。"
"而要做到这一点，便意味着粉碎你的叛乱。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:895
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You poor fool... can you not guess what horrors will come with a kin-slayer "
"on the throne? Sometimes we must fight not just for the people of today, but "
"for the people who will come after."
msgstr ""
"可怜的你...你难道看不出，让弑亲者登上王座，将招致何等恐怖的灾祸吗？有时，我们"
"战斗并非仅为了今日的子民，更是为了那些将踏足未来的后来者。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:899
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I should finish you off, but your heart is in the right place. I cannot bear "
"to slay a righteous man. Begone."
msgstr "我本欲将你彻底终结，然汝心向义。吾实不忍杀害这般正直之士。速速离去。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:917
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your sword has failed you, knight of Wesnoth! Now use your ears instead, and "
"hear the truth about our King Garard’s death!"
msgstr ""
"你的剑已背叛了你，韦诺的骑士！如今且用你的双耳倾听，来知晓我们国王伽拉德之死"
"的真相！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Swordsman
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:922
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Spare me the theatrics, Deoran. I know Eldred’s the one who took down the "
"old tyrant."
msgstr "省省那些虚张声势吧，德欧兰。我清楚是埃雷德拿下了那个老暴君。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Swordsman
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:927
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But gold is gold, and the prince has offered my wife and me a whole lot of "
"it to stick with the “official” story.\n"
"\n"
"Prince Eldred knows how to reward his allies. Give up now, accept the blame, "
"and he might even let you spend the rest of your days back in exile instead "
"of prison."
msgstr ""
"但金子就是金子，那位亲王慷慨地给了我和妻子一大笔钱，让我们配合这“官方”的说"
"法。\n"
"埃雷德亲王懂得如何奖赏他的盟友。现在投降，背下这口黑锅，他或许会大发慈悲，让"
"你余生在流放中度日，而非囹圄之中。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:933
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Garard was no hero, but you, soldier, are a villain. May your heirs prove "
"wiser than you were."
msgstr "伽拉德绝非英雄，而你，士兵，却是个恶棍。愿你的后嗣比你更明智些。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Shock Trooper
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:953
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(<i>spits</i>) Traitor. Kill me if you must, but I will never betray my "
"country."
msgstr "（啐）叛徒。若要杀我，尽管动手，但我至死也不会背弃我的祖国。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:957
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My comrade-in-arms, you already have. Look around! Eldred commands you to "
"fight and die on his behalf, while he himself has fled the battlefield.\n"
"\n"
"Are these the actions of an orphaned son, filled with a righteous desire for "
"vengeance? Or is this a scheming usurper, pitting his kingdom against itself "
"while he watches from a safe distance?"
msgstr ""
"我的并肩战友，你已看到了。环顾四周吧！埃雷德命令你为他赴死，而他自己却已逃离"
"战场。\n"
"\n"
"这难道是一个失去双亲的孤儿，满怀正义复仇之心所做出的举动吗？还是说，这正是一"
"个阴险的篡位者，在安全之处冷眼旁观，任由自己的王国自相残杀呢？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:963
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You know me, Sir Grey; we have fought side by side for many years now. Do "
"you truly believe that I would conspire with Delfador to assassinate the "
"king?"
msgstr ""
"阁下熟知我，格雷爵士；多年来我们并肩作战。您当真以为，我会与德法多大师合谋行"
"刺国王吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Shock Trooper
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:974
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I <i>thought</i> I knew you... I’m just not sure anymore. Who speaks the "
"truth? Maybe I need to get back to Dan’Tonk, away from all this fighting, "
"and take time to think. Men, let’s get out of here!"
msgstr ""
"我曾<em>以为</em>我了解你……但我如今已无法确定。究竟谁在说真话？或许我该回到丹"
"·通克，远离这场无休止的争斗，静下心来好好想想。伙计们，撤！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Shock Trooper
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:981
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I <i>thought</i> I knew you... I’m just not sure anymore. Who speaks the "
"truth? Maybe I need to get back to Dan’Tonk, away from all this fighting, "
"and take time to think."
msgstr ""
"我<b>以为</b>我认识你……可现在，我反倒不确定了。究竟谁在说真话？或许我该回到丹"
"·唐克，远离这一切战火，静下心来好好想想。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Master Bowman
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1002
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Wait, please don’t kill me Deoran! I know that you would never betray "
"Garard, but what do you expect me to do about it!? If even the king can be "
"killed, what hope do I have if I speak up?"
msgstr ""
"且慢！求您莫杀我，德欧兰！我深知您绝不会背叛伽拉德，可面对此情此景，叫我如何"
"自处？！连国王尚且难逃一死，若我直言相告，又怎敢妄存一线生机？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1006
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Then stand alongside me, and we will fight together for the truth! Eldred’s "
"lies cannot be allowed to spread."
msgstr "那么，请与我并肩而立！我们将为了真理而战，绝不容许埃雷德的谎言蔓延！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Master Bowman
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1011
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fighting together with you didn’t do the king much good, did it? No, my "
"company and I are getting back to Tath while we still have the chance!"
msgstr ""
"与阁下并肩作战，并未给国王带来多少益处，不是吗？不，趁现在还来得及，我和我的"
"队伍就要返回塔斯了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1028
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Stand down! Hold your sword and hear me out! By the very Sceptre itself, I "
"swear I did not kill the king!"
msgstr "退下！收起你的剑，听我解释！以圣火权杖之名起誓，我绝非弑君之人！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Duelist
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1033
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Wait, what!? King Garard is dead!? I heard a commotion in camp and sent my "
"fighters to help — how did the king die? What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""
"等等，什么？！伽拉德国王竟已身亡？！我方才在营地听得一阵喧哗，遂遣部众前去支"
"援——这究竟是何缘由？你又为何在此？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1037
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your ignorance is truly a relief to hear, for Prince Eldred has slain the "
"king, and blamed me for the fell deed! I have been fighting most fiercely "
"against Eldred and his allies. If you are in any shape to help, I could "
"sorely use your aid."
msgstr ""
"听闻阁下对此一无所知，倒也不失为一种慰藉。毕竟，埃雷德王子已弑杀君王，并将这"
"滔天罪行归咎于我！自那以来，我始终与埃雷德及其同党殊死搏斗。若您尚有余力，恳"
"请施以援手，此战局正需您的鼎力相助。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. said by a male Duelist
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1042
#, fuzzy
msgid "I— yes, of course! Anything I can do."
msgstr "我——是的，当然！凡我所能，定当竭力相助！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1068
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That’s the last of the leaders. Eldred has been deprived of his entire "
"northern force! Well done, well done all!"
msgstr ""
"领袖们已全部落网！埃雷德已失去了他所有的北方兵力！干得好，干得好，诸位！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1073
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All that now remains is for us to hold as long as possible, and be a "
"nuisance to Eldred’s orcish allies! The longer we survive, the longer "
"Delfador will have to prepare!"
msgstr ""
"眼下我们要做的，便是竭尽全力死守此地，成为埃雷德兽人盟友的心腹大患！我们生存"
"得越久，德法多大圣便有更多的时间筹备！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1081
#, fuzzy
msgid "Survive as long as possible (bonus gold next scenario)."
msgstr "尽可能长久地生存（下一关获得额外金币奖励）。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Ghuvog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1152
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’d better keep your human-queen’s promise of tribute, worms! Chief Ghuvog "
"is not cheap to buy; you swore to me that Fort Garard would burn to the "
"ground!"
msgstr ""
"你最好遵守你那人类王后的纳贡承诺，蠕虫！古沃格酋长可不是谁都能轻易收买的；你"
"曾向我发誓，伽拉德要塞必将被付之一炬！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: role=ghuvog_friend
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1156
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Yeah, I want revenge for our defeat and humiliation! It’s time for heads to "
"roll!"
msgstr "“没错，我们要为那场惨败与奇耻大辱复仇！现在，该让敌人的脑袋落地了！”"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1160
msgid ""
"<i><b>Just</b></i> the rebels, beast — remember our deal. Pledge enough "
"warriors into my service and you shall be rewarded most generously once "
"Mother and I have consolidated our control."
msgstr ""

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1208
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Eldred has betrayed Wesnoth’s strife to the orcish clans. With grunts "
"swarming along the riverbank, the road east to Delfador is no longer safe. "
"There can be no more escape."
msgstr ""
"埃雷德已出卖了韦诺的纷争，将其转交兽人各部。如今兽人嘶吼着沿河岸蜂拥而至，通"
"往德法多之路已不再安全。已无路可逃。"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1213
msgid "The orcs are back! There’s hordes of them!"
msgstr "兽人卷土重来了！他们铺天盖地而来！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1217
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At ease, soldier. We’ve made a deal. They’re here to help us fight the "
"rebels."
msgstr "放松些，士兵。我们已达成协定。他们前来协助我们镇压叛军。"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1222
msgid "We’re working with orcs? But, your father—"
msgstr "我们竟要与兽人联手？可是，你父亲——"

#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1226
msgid "My father is <i><b>dead</b></i>, soldier. Let the beasts through."
msgstr "我的父亲已<i><b>死</b></i>，士兵。放那些野兽进来吧。"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1236
msgid "Defeat as many enemy leaders as possible (bonus gold next scenario)."
msgstr "击败尽可能多的敌方首领（可获得额外金币奖励用于下一场景）。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. "trog" is a made-up slur referring to an orc
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1275
#, fuzzy
msgid "Filthy trog. I don’t trust you, whatever Eldred says."
msgstr "卑劣的兽渣。无论埃雷德说什么，我都不信你。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1279
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re lucky your boss is paying us off, weakling. We’ve free reign to "
"pillage any town that resists his rule, so keep your mouth shut or your home "
"will be next."
msgstr ""
"算你运气好，你的老板正在向我们付钱，弱者。我们有权洗劫任何反抗他统治的城镇，"
"所以把嘴闭紧，否则下一个被毁的就是你的家园。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1351
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Agony! My arm goes limp, I can fight no longer. Any allies yet standing, "
"scatter, scatter to the hills! It is me they will chase, not you."
msgstr ""
"剧痛！我的臂膀已无力动弹，再也无法战斗。凡尚存之盟友，速速散开，退入山峦之"
"中！他们追逐的将是我，而非尔等。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1355
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And as for me, well, I may have cut things rather closer than I had planned. "
"But what’s done is done — my thoughts must now turn to flight. Make haste, "
"my loyal steed!"
msgstr ""
"至于我嘛，哼，或许我这次把步子踩得比预想的还要险。但事已至此——我的心思如今只"
"系于逃亡一途。快些走，我忠诚的坐骑！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1361
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Agony! My arm goes limp, I can fight no longer. This may be cutting things "
"rather closer than I had planned, but what’s done is done."
msgstr ""
"剧痛！我的手臂已然瘫软，再也无法挥动武器。这或许比我所预想的更为凶险，但事已"
"至此，悔之晚矣。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1365
#, fuzzy
msgid "My thoughts must now turn to flight: make haste, my loyal steed!"
msgstr "此刻，我唯有逃遁一途：快些，我忠良的坐骑！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1409
#, fuzzy
msgid "(grins)"
msgstr "（咧嘴一笑）"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1414
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Well, well, if it isn’t Deoran the exile, one-time commander of the South "
"Guard; a soldier to the very end. I’ve heard all about you, you know. A "
"perfect example of who not to be."
msgstr ""
"哎呀呀，若我没看错，那便是流亡者德欧兰，昔日的南境守备指挥官；一位至死都是士"
"兵的人。我对你可是了如指掌，你知道。你便是“不可成为之人”的完美典范。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#. "black bottle" foreshadowing
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1419
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Did you really think you could win? Even if you had bested my army — yes, "
"it’s <b><i>my</i></b> army now — I now carry with me so much magic that I’ll "
"never have to lose another fight."
msgstr ""
"你真以为你能赢？即便你战胜了我的大军——是的，现在这是<b><i>我的</i></b>大军——"
"我也已掌握如此浩瀚的魔力，从此再也不会输掉任何一场战斗。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1424
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At last the usurper dares to face me, now that I am too injured for battle. "
"He knows his actions are unforgivable. He knows he cannot face me in a fair "
"fight."
msgstr ""
"篡位者终于敢直面我了，尽管我已重伤无力再战。他深知自己的所作所为绝无宽恕之可"
"能，他也明白，在公平的较量中，他无法战胜我。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1428
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I also know you’re a man of your word, so I’m going to give you a choice. "
"You can surrender, leave Wesnoth, and swear to never again raise arms up "
"against my rule."
msgstr ""
"我也知你是言出必行之人，故而容你择一良途。你只需投降，离去韦诺王国，并立誓永"
"不再举兵反抗我的统治。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1432
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Or you can fight, die, and have your corpse hoisted upon the walls of Weldyn "
"as a warning to others. Which will it be, exile?"
msgstr ""
"或是选择战斗，战死沙场，让你的尸身被高高悬在韦尔丹城的城墙之上，以警示他人。"
"那么，流亡者啊，你意下如何？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1436
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"More than anything does my spirit yearn to go on fighting, to risk it all on "
"a chance at vanquishing the one responsible for all this wretched "
"destruction!"
msgstr ""
"相较于一切，我的灵魂最渴望的便是继续奋战，为了那一丝战胜造成这一切悲惨毁灭之"
"人的机会，而赌上一切！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1440
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But my heart remembers better places, happier times. There are... people I "
"wish to speak to, things I have left unsaid..."
msgstr ""
"但我的心铭记着更美好的地方，更快乐的时光。那里……有我想要交谈的人，有未尽之"
"言……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1444
#, fuzzy
msgid "Prince Eldred, I lay down my arms and accept your offer of surrender."
msgstr "埃雷德亲王，我放下武器，接受您的受降提议。"

#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1467
msgid "Idiot."
msgstr "蠢货。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1475
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Not a deceitful bone in his body. I didn’t even have to drink the potion. "
"That’s... a relief."
msgstr "他身上毫无半分虚伪。我甚至不必饮用那剂魔药。这……真令人宽慰。"

#. [message]: speaker=Kestrel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1479
msgid "The traitor is vanquished! Now hail, hail to your new king!"
msgstr "叛徒已被征服！现在高呼，高呼新王万岁！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: id=$speaker1_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1493
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hail King Eldred!"
msgstr "万岁，埃雷德国王！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: id=$speaker2_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1504
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hail, long live King Eldred!"
msgstr "万岁，吾王埃雷德！"

#. [message]: id=$speaker3_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1515
msgid "Long live the king!"
msgstr "国王万岁！"

#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13_Revelry_Revisited.cfg:1523
msgid "Yes. Long live the king."
msgstr "是。国王万岁。"

#. [scenario]: id=13x_The_King_is_Dead
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:6
msgid "The King is Dead"
msgstr "国王死了"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:112
#, fuzzy
msgid "Gods... what a fool I have been."
msgstr "诸神……我竟如此愚钝。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:117
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Whitefangs, Blackcrests. Saurians, Arand. I really thought I was doing "
"something great; fighting the good fight for king and country."
msgstr ""
"白牙氏族，黑冠部族。蜥蜴人，阿兰德。我当真以为自己在成就一番伟业，为国王与国"
"家而战，行那正义之战。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:121
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But when it really mattered, I couldn’t see past my own ego. What kind of "
"man was I? What kind of <b><i>friend</i></b> was I?"
msgstr ""
"但当真正紧要关头来临时，我却无法超越自身的 ego。我究竟是个什么样的男人？我又"
"是个什么样的<b><i>挚友</i></b>？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$horselord_id
#. said by a male Horseman-line or Cavalryman-line unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:126
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"’tis a dark day indeed. Orcs rampage across the countryside, pillaging and "
"looting, while the false King Eldred does nothing. Worse than nothing: he "
"marches on our own settlements, consolidating his power!"
msgstr ""
"当真是个黑暗之日。兽人肆意劫掠乡野，烧杀抢掠，而那伪王埃雷德却无动于衷。不，"
"何止无动于衷：他竟挥军直逼我方据点，以巩固其窃据的权位！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$horselord_id
#. said by a male Horseman-line or Cavalryman-line unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:131
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Our king has perished, our kingdom in peril! Are we to stand idly by and "
"watch it fall, o’ great Delfador?"
msgstr ""
"吾王已陨，王国危在旦夕！伟大的德法多，难道我们要袖手旁观，静看其倾覆吗？"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. $horselord_name is a male Horseman-line or Cavalryman-line unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:137
msgid ""
"I’m not “The Great” anymore, $horselord_name. Was I ever? Everything I ever "
"achieved was either a lie or has already been undone."
msgstr ""
"我早已不再是“大师”了，$horselord_name。我当真有过那么伟大吗？我所成就的一切，"
"要么是一场谎言，要么早已化为乌有。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:141
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Our company is strong, but what power have we to lay low the walls of "
"Weldyn? To wreak fire and lightning through the streets until finally I "
"excise the festering boil at the heart of all this madness? If only."
msgstr ""
"我军势盛，然而，何来神力能推倒温德恩的城墙？何来雷霆烈焰，焚遍街巷，直至我将"
"这疯狂核心的毒瘤彻底切除？若能如此，实乃幸事。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:147
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I was warned about this... <i>“Bestow not destruction, but the gleaming "
"light of truth instead”</i>; <i>“the line of kings sundered”</i> — what can "
"the seer have been referring to if not my attack on Arand?\n"
"\n"
"Even now, still I understand nothing! <i>“From the barren throne will rise "
"an angel of ashes”</i> — <i>“The nameless son and the ashen daughter”</i> — "
"what nightmares are these that are prophesied to arise from my failure? The "
"coming years will be dark indeed."
msgstr ""
"我曾收到过对此的警示……<i>“切勿降下毁灭，当予真理之璀璨光辉”</i>；<i>“王族血脉"
"已然断裂”</i>——先知所言若非指向我对阿兰德的攻击，那又究竟是何意？\n"
"\n"
"即便至今，我依然对此一无所获！<i>“从荒芜的王座上，将升腾起灰烬之天使”</i>——"
"<i>“无名之子与灰之之女”</i>——这些由我的失败所预言的噩梦，究竟是何等光景？未来"
"的岁月，必将黯淡无光。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:153
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh seer, what I would give for another chance! I obeyed my friend, and in "
"doing so betrayed him! And now there is nothing left."
msgstr ""
"哦，先知啊，我愿用一切换取重来的机会！我曾顺从挚友，却因此背叛了他！如今，一"
"切皆已成空。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. "no need to be so glum" is what Delfador says in S01
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:169
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, I have found you at last! “Nothing left?” There’s no need to be so "
"glum."
msgstr "德法多，我终于找到您了！“已无路可退？”不必如此愁云惨淡。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:173
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Master!? I’d no idea you survived the coup! But you come far too late. I "
"fear it’s all already over."
msgstr ""
"大师！我竟不知您竟能在那场政变中幸存！但您来得太晚了。恐怕一切早已尘埃落定。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:178
#, fuzzy
msgid "I heard your earlier words to the horselord. Do not think of giving up!"
msgstr "我曾听闻你先前对那位马背上的王者的言语。切莫生出放弃之念！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:182
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The boy I raised always sought the approval of others: from your peers, from "
"your master, from your king. Now the darkness rings close, and at last you "
"are alone — even I have grown old, and can speak for you no longer."
msgstr ""
"我曾抚育的男孩，总在寻求他人的认可：来自同侪，来自师长，来自君王。如今黑暗迫"
"近，你已孑然一身——即便我也已老去，再也无法为你代言。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:186
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The time has come to choose. Who are you, Delfador? Are you nobody; a tired "
"young student; a hanger-on fawning at the feet of his betters? Or are you "
"Delfador the Great, no-one’s servant and his own man! CHOOSE, apprentice!"
msgstr ""
"抉择的时刻已到。德法多，你是谁？你不过是个无名之辈？一个疲惫的年轻学徒？还是"
"一个只会对权贵摇尾乞怜的闲散之徒？抑或是那个“德法多大师”——不隶属于任何人，只"
"属于他自己的传奇人物！学徒，做出你的选择！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:190
#, fuzzy
msgid "Look, Methor, it’s not as easy as saying a few words..."
msgstr "瞧，梅瑟，事情没那么简单，绝非几句咒语便能了事……"

#. [message]: speaker=$horselord_id
#. said by a male Horseman-line or Cavalryman-line unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:212
msgid "Well? Shall we fight?"
msgstr "那么？我们要开战吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:222
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We shall fight! The usurper Eldred is on the march, and on the march he is "
"exposed. This time, we need no king nor country to guide our hand. I know "
"what is right, and I will make it so."
msgstr ""
"我们将奋起抗争！篡位者埃雷德正率军行进，而这正是他暴露无遗之时。这一次，无需"
"国王与国度来指引我们的双手。我知晓何为正义，必将将其化为现实。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:226
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Scouts, take my seal! Spread the word: all of Wesnoth must know of Eldred’s "
"treachery. Whether it takes one year or a hundred, I <b><i>will</i></b> see "
"the throne of Wesnoth restored."
msgstr ""
"斥候，取我的印信！传令四方：韦诺全境必须知晓埃雷德的背叛。无论需耗一载光阴，"
"抑或百年岁月，我必<b><i>将</i></b>令韦诺王座重现光辉！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/13x_The_King_is_Dead.cfg:230
#, fuzzy
msgid "The rest of you, make ready! We march to kill the king."
msgstr "诸位，即刻整装待发！我们此行，便是为了诛杀暴君。"

#. [scenario]: id=14_Long_Live_the_Queen
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:6
msgid "Long Live the Queen"
msgstr "女王万岁"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:25
msgid "Delfador’s Rebels"
msgstr "德法多的反抗军"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:73
msgid "King Eldred"
msgstr "埃雷德国王"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:232
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A heroic duel, Delfador? Really? You forget that I have an army on my side."
msgstr ""
"一场英雄间的决斗？德法多大师？你是认真的吗？别忘了，我身后可拥有一支大军。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:324
#, fuzzy
msgid "Foxtail Outriders"
msgstr "狐尾斥候骑兵"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:338
msgid "Blackcrest Outriders"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:572
msgid "No! Methor... Don’t die!"
msgstr "不！梅瑟……不要死！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:576
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, my sweet, wonderful apprentice... I couldn’t be more proud of "
"you..."
msgstr "德法多，我挚爱而卓越的学徒……我对你再骄傲不过了……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. callback to S01 where Methor complains about Delfador not learning a seeker spell
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:598
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Look at the length of that column! The prince — the king, I suppose — must "
"have picked up more soldiers at Dan’Tonk, when he forced the magistrate to "
"swear fealty. Your seeker spell was excellent, Delfador; we’ve been able to "
"find and intercept Eldred before he could turn anyone else to his cause."
msgstr ""
"看看那支队伍的阵线有多长！那位王子——或者说，依我猜，那位国王——定是在丹·唐克迫"
"使地方官宣誓效忠时，又收编了不少士兵。你那寻踪法术施展得极妙，德法多；正是凭"
"借它，我们才得以在艾雷德拉拢更多部众之前，将其拦截并一举擒获。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:602
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Boss, how’s we supposed to fight that many!? Even if we could, what about "
"Queen Asheviere back in Weldyn?"
msgstr ""
"老大，我们拿什么去对付这么多敌人？就算打得赢，那留在韦德因的艾什薇尔王后又该"
"怎么办？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$horselord_id
#. said by a male Horseman-line or Cavalryman-line unit
#. "reigns" is a pun - "reigns of power", but also the kind of reins that you use to control a horse (this is a mounted unit speaking)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:608
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Indeed! Word is she’s killed half of the court and paid off the rest; the "
"remaining lords of the city are loyal only to her! Eldred may be king, but "
"Asheviere holds the reins."
msgstr ""
"果然！据闻她已屠戮半数朝臣，收买了余下之人；城中其余领主皆唯她是从！埃雷德虽"
"为国王，却由艾什薇尔执掌缰绳。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:612
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We don’t have to fight the entire army or deal with Weldyn. The capital is "
"too well-defended for us to sack outright — Eldred is the objective here."
msgstr ""
"我们不必强攻整支大军，也无须攻克韦德林。那座都城固若金汤，难以直接攻陷——真正"
"的目标，是埃雷德。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:616
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Once the truth gets out about Garard’s death, we’ll have enough allies to "
"liberate Weldyn and more besides. But only if we can stop Eldred here and "
"now — can prove to the watchers that this coup is not yet over; that justice "
"and honor and hope still live in Wesnoth! That’s our goal today."
msgstr ""
"一旦加拉德之死真相大白，我们必将汇聚足够的盟友，不仅解放韦诺，更将扫除更多阴"
"霾。但这唯有此刻、此地，我们便能遏住埃雷德；唯有向守望者们证明，这场政变尚未"
"尽终；唯有让正义、荣誉与希望仍在韦诺存续！这正是我们今日的目标。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:621
#, fuzzy
msgid "Look sharp, I think they’ve spotted us!"
msgstr "小心点，我想他们已经发现我们了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=$companion_id
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:622
#, fuzzy
msgid "female^Look sharp, I think they’ve spotted us!"
msgstr "女^小心点，我想他们发现我们了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:630
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, welcome! I was wondering if we’d get an appearance from you old "
"has-been! ’fraid you’re not as popular with Mother and me as you were with "
"old Garard."
msgstr ""
"德法多，欢迎！我正琢磨着会不会请得动你这位老朽登台呢！恐怕你在我母亲和我这"
"里，已不像当年在老伽拉德那里那般吃香了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:634
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Opposing me is hopeless, old mage. But it’s not too late to save yourself — "
"surrender now, disband your little rebel rabble, and we can tell the men it "
"was all a big misunderstanding."
msgstr ""
"对抗我毫无希望，老法师。但想保全自己还不算太晚——即刻投降，解散你那群小小的叛"
"军暴徒，我们可以对外宣称那不过是一场巨大的误会。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:638
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Just lay down your staff and greet me with open arms. You can even have your "
"old title back! “Delfador the Great”, High Advisor to the Crown — don’t you "
"agree that has a nice ring to it?"
msgstr ""
"放下法杖，敞开双臂欢迎我便是。你甚至能重获旧日尊号——“德法多大师”，王国首席顾"
"问。这般名号，难道不正是你心中所愿吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:642
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I am no longer so foolish as to be tempted by <b><i>that</i></b>, young "
"prince! Enough blood has been spilled on your behalf; stop this madness and "
"give up the throne, or I shall make you."
msgstr ""
"我早已不再愚蠢，竟会受<b><i>那东西</i></b>的蛊惑，年轻的王子！为你而流的血已"
"足够多；快停止这疯狂，交出王位，否则——我便亲手替你摘掉那顶王冠！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:646
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh no, I don’t think so. You forget you’re speaking to your king, old man. "
"Soldiers, attack! ATTACK!"
msgstr ""
"哦，不，我可没这么想。老家伙，你忘了此刻正对着你的国王说话吧。士兵们，进攻！"
"进攻！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:656
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1061
msgid "Defeat Eldred"
msgstr "击败埃雷德"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:736
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Eldred, you know full well that your father and I were close! Is this what "
"he would have wanted? His kingdom turned against itself, his townships "
"pillaged by orcs? He had hope; a future for Wesnoth! A future for you!"
msgstr ""
"埃雷德，你心里再清楚不过：你父亲与我曾情同手足！难道这就是他所期许的吗？王国"
"内部自相残杀，城镇遭兽人劫掠？他曾满怀希望；他盼望着韦诺的明天！盼望着你的未"
"来！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:740
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A future for me? I can count on one hand the times the old tyrant had "
"anything kind to say about me."
msgstr ""
"为我争取一个未来？哼，那老暴君对我说过哪怕半句好话，恐怕我都能用一只手数得过"
"来。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:744
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I wasn’t going to wait around to be disinherited, or worse. It was always "
"going to be him or me — I just beat him to the finish."
msgstr ""
"我可不会坐以待毙，等着被剥夺继承权，甚至更惨。结果本就非他即我——我只是抢先一"
"步冲过了终点。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:748
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fool. I will not bandy words with whatever madness has taken root inside "
"your mind, Eldred. Garard was harsh; I cannot deny that. But you’re a fool "
"if you think he ever felt anything but love for you."
msgstr ""
"蠢货。我绝不会与你脑海中滋生出的疯狂虚与委蛇，埃雷德。伽拉德的手段固然严苛，"
"我承认这一点。但若你认为他对你从未有过一丝怜爱，那你才是真正的蠢货。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:755
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’m no fool, Delfador. Day and night, my parents fought. Whether said in "
"truth or in anger, there are some things my father can never take back."
msgstr ""
"我并非愚钝，德法多大师。日日夜夜，双亲争执不休。无论那是出于真心还是愤怒，有"
"些事，我父亲永远无法收回。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:759
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And don’t think that I have any illusions about what sort of snake Mother is "
"either. I know, believe me. But she’s the snake who’s made me king, and "
"that’s good enough."
msgstr ""
"别以为我对母后那蛇蝎心肠的本性毫无察觉。我清楚，请相信我。但她正是那条将我推"
"上王位的毒蛇，这就足够了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#. this refers to the events of S05 The Deceiver and S06 Ring of Swords
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:771
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This wasn’t the first time Mother’s gone after Garard, you know. In the "
"early days of the war, she betrayed his plans to the Whitefangs; fled to the "
"orcs while they surrounded you and him both."
msgstr ""
"别以为这是母亲第一次对伽拉德动手。你知道的，在战争初期，她就把他的计划泄露给"
"了白牙氏族；当你们二人被兽人包围之时，她竟逃奔到了兽人那边。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:775
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You and Deoran brought her back, of course, and Lionel fought Garard free of "
"the orcs. My childhood would have been so different if things had "
"succeeded..."
msgstr ""
"你与德欧兰将她带回，而莱昂内尔则力战，将伽拉德从兽人手中救出。倘若此事得逞，"
"我的童年本会截然不同……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:787
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’m surprised you haven’t given up yet, wizard! But you’re no stranger to "
"hopeless fights, are you — you bested Malal, escaped the frozen north, "
"scattered our saurians."
msgstr ""
"我倒惊讶于你竟尚未放弃，法师！但你也并非第一次面对必败之局，不是吗？你曾击败"
"玛拉尔，逃离极北冻土，更将我族蜥蜴人驱散四方。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:791
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Malal was clever; <i>really</i> clever, and determined too. No-one but "
"Mother knows what Garard did to earn Malal’s ire, but the two of them would "
"stop at nothing to see Garard dead and his reputation destroyed. Tricking "
"the saurians and orcs into working together, getting Lionel sent away, "
"pitting Garard against Arand..."
msgstr ""
"玛拉尔此人颇有心计，<i> truly</i> 心机深沉，且意志决绝。除了母后，无人知晓伽"
"拉德究竟做了何事才招致玛拉尔的滔天怒火，但这二人为了将伽拉德置于死地、使其身"
"败名裂，必将不择手段。他们诱使蜥蜴人与兽人联手，将莱昂内尔调离，更挑起伽拉德"
"与阿兰德之间的争斗……"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:795
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Delfador, you weren’t supposed to survive Malal. You weren’t supposed to "
"survive <i><b>any</b></i> of that."
msgstr ""
"德法多，你本不该在玛拉尔手中生还。你本不该从那一切之中生还——<i><b>任何</b></"
"i>一次。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:799
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Would that more had survived along with me, Eldred. Would that I had "
"listened to Deoran, would that I had understood the seer! Had I been but a "
"little wiser, so many lives might yet have been saved."
msgstr ""
"若能与我一同幸存的人多一些就好了，埃雷德。若能当初听从德欧兰的劝告，若能理解"
"那位先知的预言，那该多好。若我当时能再聪慧些许，如此多的生命或许便得以保全。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:803
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I can never atone for the lives I cost, but I can yet honor them through my "
"actions. And right now, honoring them means stopping you."
msgstr ""
"我永无法赎偿我夺去的那些性命，但我仍能以行动告慰他们。而此刻，告慰他们便意味"
"着阻止你。"

#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:849
msgid "NO!"
msgstr "不！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:853
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It’s over, Eldred. Down on your knees, now! The rest of you; get back! BACK, "
"or you’ll have to find yet another king!"
msgstr ""
"一切结束了，埃雷德！跪下！至于你们其他人，退后！退后！否则……你们就得去找别的"
"国王了！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:857
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I didn’t come all this way just to fail now... not at the hand of some cheap "
"conjurer. No, I prepared for this. After my failed attack on Arand, I "
"took... precautions."
msgstr ""
"我千里迢迢至此，绝不可能在此刻失败……尤其不是败给某个三流幻术师的手中。不，我"
"早已为此……做好了防范。在我对阿兰德的袭击失败后，我便采取了……必要的预防措施。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:861
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"They say this elixir came all the way from the Old Continent, Delfador. "
"Persuading Malal to give it up wasn’t easy.\n"
"\n"
"You like magic so much? Once I drink from Jevyan’s Cup, I’ll have enough "
"magic to turn you all to dust!"
msgstr ""
"他们都说，这灵药可是远从旧大陆辗转而来，德法多大师。想要说服玛拉尔交出它，可"
"绝非易事。\n"
"\n"
"你如此迷恋魔法？待我饮下杰文之杯，便足以施展毁天灭地之术，将你们统统化为尘"
"埃！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. liches are skeletal; they don't have blood. This is a consumable artifact of unknown composition, probably captured/extracted from lich-lord Jevyan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:868
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Is that— are you holding <i>lich’s blood</i>!? How— Put it down, Eldred!"
msgstr "德法多：那——你手里拿的是<巫妖之血>！？怎么……把它放下，埃雷德！"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:872
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Whatever you do, don’t you dare drink it! We have no idea what will happen! "
"Don’t you dare, Eldred! ELDRED!"
msgstr ""
"无论发生什么，你绝不敢饮下它！我们根本不知道会发生什么！你绝不敢，埃雷德！埃"
"雷德！"

#. [unit]: id=MiddleEldred, type=King Eldred # use a new ID so events don't interfere
#. [unit]: id=HunkerEldred, type=Hunker Eldred # use a new ID so phase 1 and phase 2 events don't interfere
#. [unit]: id=FinalEldred, type=King Eldred # use a new ID so events don't interfere
#. [unit]: id=FinalEldred, type=King Eldred
#. [unit]: id=HunkerEldred, type=Hunker Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:993
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1301
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1517
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1583
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1607
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:117
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:130
msgid "Eldred"
msgstr "埃雷德"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1023
#, fuzzy
msgid "Finally, I understand."
msgstr "原来如此，我终于明白了。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1027
#, fuzzy
msgid "I can make the pain all go away. I can make everything better again."
msgstr "我能让痛楚烟消云散。我能让一切再度重归美好。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1032
#, fuzzy
msgid "...you can?"
msgstr "……你也能做到？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1049
#, fuzzy
msgid "I just need to kill everyone else first."
msgstr "我仅需先屠戮众人。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1087
#, fuzzy
msgid "Everything is so clear now. I see the past; the future."
msgstr "如今一切皆已昭然若揭。我看见了过往，亦窥见了未来。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1091
#, fuzzy
msgid "Your eyes were clouded. You could not tell the truth from the lie."
msgstr "你的双眼已被蒙蔽，无法分辨真与假。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1097
#, fuzzy
msgid "You still can’t, can you?"
msgstr "你依然做不到，是吧？"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1273
msgid "Give up."
msgstr "放弃。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1413
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your achievements are undone. Your king is dead. The ghosts of the past will "
"always haunt you, Delfador war-mage."
msgstr ""
"你的功业已付诸东流，你的君王已然陨落。过往的亡魂将永远纠缠着你，德法多，战争"
"法师。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1536
msgid "No."
msgstr "不。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1576
#, fuzzy
msgid "You really still don’t understand, do you?"
msgstr "你至今仍执迷不悟，是吗？"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1598
msgid ""
"You had your chance to change fate. Your revelation came too late. The "
"future is already written."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. prophecy callback
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1625
msgid ""
"You have no title, no country, no king. You are a failure. Alone, you are "
"nothing."
msgstr "你无头衔，无国度，无君王。你已是个失败者。孑然一身，你不过是一缕微尘。"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1685
msgid "Nothing? I am Delfador."
msgstr "没有？我是德法多。"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1689
msgid "And you are dust."
msgstr "而你们是尘土。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#. 13 kings is made-up, because 13 is an unlucky number. 12 non-Eldred kings across 500 years makes for an average 42 year reign
#. given Wesnoth's access to magical healing, a 42-year reign average seems plausible, if rather high.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1710
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Thus perishes Eldred, thirteenth king of Wesnoth.\n"
"\n"
"With him ends the story of the sons of Haldric; that unbroken line of kings "
"stretching five hundred years back to the Green Isle itself."
msgstr ""
"于是，韦诺第十三任君主埃雷德陨落。\n"
"随着他的逝去，哈尔德里克子孙的传奇亦告终结；那一条绵延五百年、直通绿岛的血脉"
"王统，至此划上句点。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1716
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The exhausted Delfador fights valiantly against Eldred’s — now Asheviere’s — "
"army, but reinforcements from Weldyn eventually repulse the beleaguered "
"rebels. Neither side wins a decisive military victory."
msgstr ""
"精疲力竭的德法多英勇地对抗着埃雷德——如今已是艾什薇尔——的军队，但来自韦诺的增"
"援最终击退了这支被困的叛军。双方均未取得决定性的军事胜利。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1720
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As word spreads of the kings’ deaths, a terrible foreboding seems to settle "
"over the Wesnothian countryside."
msgstr "随着国王死讯传遍四方，一种恐怖的预感似乎笼罩了韦诺的乡野。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/14_Long_Live_the_Queen.cfg:1724
msgid "After all, the civil war has only just begun..."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=Cave Entrance, race=mechanical
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Cave_Entrance.cfg:5
msgid "Cave Entrance"
msgstr "洞穴入口"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Cave Entrance, race=mechanical
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Cave_Entrance.cfg:15
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A crudely hewn passage into the earth, propped open by ageing wooden "
"supports."
msgstr "一条粗凿入地的通道，由陈旧的木制支架支撑着。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Prince of Wesnoth, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Arand.cfg:4
msgid "Prince of Wesnoth"
msgstr "韦诺王子"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Prince of Wesnoth, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Arand.cfg:14
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Brothers of a ruling king are traditionally titled ‘Prince’ and bequeathed "
"wide swathes of land to rule."
msgstr "统治君王的兄弟，按传统皆称亲王，并被授予大片疆土以治之。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [attack]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Arand.cfg:29
#, fuzzy
msgid "broadsword"
msgstr "阔剑"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Queen, race=human, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Asheviere.cfg:4
#, fuzzy
msgid "Queen"
msgstr "王后"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Queen, race=human, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Asheviere.cfg:14
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While some queens are influential leaders, many others have their role "
"restricted to mere social companionship.\n"
"\n"
"Nevertheless, even when she does not share political and military power with "
"the king, a queen can still take part in the kingdom’s internal politics, "
"both by influencing the royal court and through her kinship with the royal "
"family."
msgstr ""
"虽有些王后是极具影响力的领袖，但许多人的角色却仅限于充当社交伴侣。\n"
"\n"
"然而，即便她未能与君王共掌军政大权，王后仍能通过影响皇家宫廷以及与王室的亲缘"
"纽带，积极参与王国之内部政治。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L1, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L1.cfg:8
msgid "Mage"
msgstr "法师"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L1, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L1.cfg:12
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Humans have often pondered the workings of the world in which they live. "
"Some endeavor to take this beyond idle musing, to set it as the primary "
"enterprise of their lives. Any magi worthy of the title have spent at least "
"a decade in study, amassing a sum of knowledge which sets them apart from "
"other people. These men and women, who have committed themselves fully to "
"the pursuit of wisdom, stand in stark contrast to a world where few can even "
"read and write. Their ranks are filled with the children of hopeful "
"nobility, or those who sought an escape from the intellectual void of manual "
"labor.\n"
"\n"
"It is an irony that, with all their knowledge, and their unassuming monopoly "
"thereof, the collective community of magi could likely rule society, were "
"they ever to try. However, their true love is neither money, nor power, and "
"those who see the study of magic as a means to such ends often lack the very "
"conviction required for true mastery.\n"
"\n"
"Physically frail, and lacking familiarity with combat, magi do possess "
"certain arts which are of great utility in battle."
msgstr ""
"人类常沉思他们所处世界的运作法则。有些人试图超越漫无目的的冥思，将探索世界本"
"质确立为人生的首要使命。任何配得上“法师”之名的法师，都至少历经十载寒窗苦读，"
"积攒起远超常人的学识。这些全心投身于智慧追求的男女，与一个鲜少有人能读能写的"
"社会形成了鲜明对比。他们的队伍中，不乏怀抱希望的贵族子弟，也有那些渴望从体力"
"劳动的愚昧深渊中逃离的求知者。\n"
"\n"
"颇具讽刺意味的是，尽管他们掌握了渊博的知识，并独占了这门学问，若他们真有统治"
"社会的野心，便足以轻易主宰整个文明。然而，他们真正的挚爱并非财富，亦非权柄；"
"那些将魔法 merely 视为达成此类目的之手段的人，往往恰恰缺乏真正驾驭魔法所需的"
"那份坚定信念。\n"
"\n"
"法师虽体魄孱弱，且鲜少涉足战场，却也拥有某些在战斗中极具价值的奇术。"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L1.cfg:31
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L2.cfg:29
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L3.cfg:32
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L4.cfg:32
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Orcish_Adept.cfg:31
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Orcish_Shaman.cfg:31
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Orcish_Sorceress.cfg:31
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Saurian_Devotee.cfg:45
msgid "staff"
msgstr "法杖"

#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L2, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L2.cfg:8
msgid "Red Mage"
msgstr "红袍法师"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L2, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L2.cfg:12
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Upon the successful culmination of their apprenticeship, a mage is stripped "
"of the brown robes of an apprentice and given the ruddy cloak of a master. "
"The significance of this change is often lost on the peasantry, who "
"mistakenly title Master Magi as ‘Red Magi’. Likewise, the symbolism of the "
"change in colors is often mistaken to signify the mage’s ability to "
"seemingly conjure fire from nothing but thin air, a trick which, although "
"undeniably useful, is viewed by the magi themselves as a crass application "
"of their hard-won knowledge.\n"
"\n"
"Though physically frail, and untrained as warriors, the ‘Red Magi’ have a "
"number of tricks up their sleeves, including the gouts of fire which may "
"have cemented their colloquial name."
msgstr ""
"当学徒期的修业圆满达成之际，法师将褪去褐袍，披上象征大师身份的赤红斗篷。然"
"而，这一变革的深意往往被乡野平民所忽视，他们误将大法师统称为“赤红法师”。同"
"样，颜色的更迭常被误读为法师能从无中生有地召来烈火——尽管这一手段确实卓有成"
"效，但在真正的法师眼中，这不过是对来之不易的奥术知识的一种粗鄙应用。\n"
"\n"
"虽则身板孱弱，亦无战阵训练，“赤红法师”袖中却藏有数种奇技，其中那喷涌而起的烈"
"焰，或许正是使其获得这一通俗名号的缘由。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L3, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L3.cfg:8
msgid "Arch Mage"
msgstr "大法师"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L3, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L3.cfg:12
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The title of Arch Mage is traditionally conferred only after a lifetime of "
"study and achievement to match. Arch Magi are often employed in positions of "
"education, or as advisors to those sensible enough to seek the fruits of "
"their wisdom. Many tend to wealthy patrons, a profitable enterprise for both "
"as, outside of the occasional thaumaturgy or word of advice, it gives the "
"mage leave to pursue their research undisturbed. From this flows the greater "
"body of human knowledge; the sciences, the philosophies, and the arts which "
"give beauty to the world at large.\n"
"\n"
"Though not trained for any sort of combat, if need arises an Arch Mage can "
"unleash the full power of their art, something which is not to be taken "
"lightly."
msgstr ""
"大法师之职，历来唯有毕生潜心钻研、且成就斐然者方可获授。大法师常执教鞭，或出"
"任贤明之士——那些深知汲取其智慧之利者——之顾问。此类师徒往往与富商大贾结盟，乃"
"是一桩双赢之业：除偶施法术或略献良言外，大法师得以潜心治学，不受干扰。正是由"
"此，人类之宏大知识体系得以汇聚而成；那些赋予世间万象以美之科学、哲学与艺术，"
"皆源于此。\n"
"\n"
"虽未受训于战阵，但若事势所逼，大法师亦可尽释其艺术之全力，此事绝不可等闲视"
"之。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L4, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L4.cfg:8
msgid "Great Mage"
msgstr "伟大法师"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Delfador L4, race=human
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Delfador_L4.cfg:12
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Any person who is even considered for the title of Great Mage is quite "
"nearly a legend in their own time, and town criers have forcibly learnt "
"discretion in applying the title. Merit for the title is carefully "
"considered by a council of the leading magi of the age, and the conferment "
"of the title is given only by a majority vote. Regardless, anyone who is "
"seriously nominated for the honor of being called a Great Mage is, without "
"question, a master of their art, and has surpassed almost any of their peers "
"in skill.\n"
"\n"
"Though they are not warriors, by any means, the application of their art to "
"combat is something that often causes other soldiers to stand aside in awe."
msgstr ""
"凡有资格竞逐“大法师”之名者，在其时代已近乎传奇。因此，城内的传令官在以此头衔"
"相称时，不得不学会谨言慎行。该头衔的授予资格须经由当世顶尖法师组成的议会审慎"
"斟酌，唯有经多数票表决通过，方得正式授封。\n"
"\n"
"尽管如此，凡被认真提名角逐“大法师”这一殊荣者，毫无疑问皆是其领域的大师，其技"
"艺之精湛，早已凌驾于同侪之上。\n"
"\n"
"虽非战士，然其施法入战，亦常令寻常士兵肃然起敬，退避三舍。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Cavalier, race=human, description=<i>
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Deoran_Elvish.cfg:8
msgid "Veteran Cavalier"
msgstr "资深弩骑士"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Cavalier, race=human, description=<i>
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Deoran_Elvish.cfg:12
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran rides an elvish horse, and has better movement and defense in forest "
"than do most mounted human units."
msgstr "德欧兰骑乘精灵战马，在森林中的移动力与防御力优于多数人类骑兵单位。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Cavalier, race=human, description=<i>
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Deoran_Elvish.cfg:14
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A wise and skilful dignitary may eventually rise to the rank of ambassador "
"and become an official envoy of Wesnoth. Typically stationed in far-off "
"nations, these diplomats excel at negotiation and leadership, and have the "
"authority to broker treaties on behalf of the throne."
msgstr ""
"一位睿智且技艺娴熟的外交官，最终有望晋升至大使之位，成为韦诺王国的正式使节。"
"此类外交官通常驻守于遥远国度，他们擅长谈判与领导，并拥有代表王权缔结条约的权"
"柄。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Cavalier, race=human, description=<i>
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Deoran_Elvish.cfg:16
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In times of hardship, these retired commanders may be called upon to once "
"again take up their lance and fight in service of their nation. Having "
"learned from civilian life while still retaining much of their former "
"military skill, these captains are undeterred by even the most overwhelming "
"opposition."
msgstr ""
"每逢国难，这些退役的指挥官便会被重新征召，再度扬起长矛，为他们的国度而战。他"
"们在世俗生活中汲取了智慧，却依然保有昔日精湛的军事技艺，即便是面对最为压倒性"
"的敌军，他们也毫不动摇。"

#. [attack]: type=pierce
#. [attack]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Deoran_Elvish.cfg:45
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Garard.cfg:33
msgid "lance"
msgstr "枪"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [attack]: type=impact
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Deoran_Elvish.cfg:57
#, fuzzy
msgid "trample"
msgstr "践踏"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [attack]: type=pierce
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Deoran_Elvish.cfg:65
#, fuzzy
msgid "crossbow"
msgstr "弩"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
