#. [unit_type]: id=Unarmed Eldred, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Eldred_Hunker.cfg:7
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Human_Eldred_Magic.cfg:4
