# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Saurian Juvenile, race=lizard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Saurian_Juvenile.cfg:15
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"These young saurians are less than a year old, and are too weak and infirm "
"to hunt or fight. Older Juveniles may tend to a few basic duties within "
"their clutch, but are still defenceless in combat. As these saurians grow "
"older, they will quickly learn to fend for themselves and become fully grown "
"adults by the age of three."
msgstr ""
"这些年轻的蜥蜴人尚不满一岁，体弱多病，既无力狩猎，也无法参战。年长一些的幼年"
"蜥蜴或许能在巢群中承担少量基础杂务，但在战场上依旧毫无自保之力。待其年岁渐"
"长，它们将迅速学会独立生存，并在三岁时彻底成长为成年蜥蜴人。"

# Translated by openai with model qwen3.5-35b-a3b.
#. [unit_type]: id=Saurian Spike, race=lizard, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Saurian_Young.cfg:23
#, fuzzy
