#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/units/Saurian_Young.cfg:37
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"These young saurians are still learning to wield a proper spear, and have "
"not yet attained the skills of their elders. They are skilled enough to hunt "
"small animals, but are still unprepared for a true battle, fighting only on "
"the most dire occasions."
msgstr ""
"这些年轻的蜥蜴人尚在学习如何挥舞长矛，尚未掌握其长辈那般精湛的技艺。他们虽有"
"狩猎小动物的本领，却仍不足以应对真正的战事，唯有在最为危急的关头才会拔剑相"
"向。"

